er%20living%20in%20New%20York%20was%20a%20serious%20whiplash.%20My%20childhood%20bedroom%20suddenly%20felt%20smaller%20and%20quieter%2C%20and%20the%20absence%20of%20my%20college%20friends%20made%20the%20town%20feel%20emptier%20than%20I%20remembered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221089%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20author%20in%20her%20college%20graduation%20gown%20under%20a%20sign%20that%20reads%20new%20york%20university%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69978c26a645d1188189a3f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22722%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20had%20to%20move%20back%20home%20after%20NYU.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Diana%20Solis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20parts%20I%20am%20grateful%20for%2C%20though.%20After%20almost%20four%20years%20of%20seeing%20them%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20times%20a%20year%2C%20I%20finally%20get%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20my%20parents.%20I%20also%20hated%20the%20harsh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhuge-winter-storm-east-coast-heavy-snow-travel-delays-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEast%20Coast%20winters%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20definitely%20do%20not%20miss%20schlepping%20my%20Trader%20Joe's%20groceries%20down%2010%20blocks%20and%20then%20up%20four%20flights%20of%20stairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pace%20here%20is%20gentler%2C%20the%20streets%20are%20quieter%2C%20and%20while%20it's%20not%20Manhattan%2C%20it's%20given%20me%20a%20space%20to%20breathe%20and%20reflect%20in%20ways%20I%20couldn't%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVisiting%20New%20York%20every%20few%20months%20reminds%20me%20why%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20city%2C%20but%20living%20at%20home%20has%20also%20shown%20me%20that%20slowing%20down%20is%20not%20the%20same%20thing%20as%20standing%20still.%20I've%20been%20creative%20with%20my%20career%2C%20focusing%20on%20writing%2C%20networking%2C%20and%20mentoring%2C%20while%20appreciating%20the%20small%20moments%20I%20took%20for%20granted%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c96610d-083b-4b76-8ccc-00a6d3ea32ed%5C%22%3EI'm%20still%20learning%20a%20lot%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sometimes%20catch%20myself%20wondering%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20did%20this%20differently%2C%20would%20I%20be%20living%20and%20working%20in%20New%20York%20by%20now%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20to%20constantly%20remind%20myself%20that%20I%20am%20only%2023%20and%20I%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20life%20to%20live.%20New%20York%20will%20always%20be%20there.%20There%20have%20been%20many%20times%20when%20I%20doubted%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecent-college-graduate-still-job-hunting-finding-self-outside-work-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecareer%20in%20journalism%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20considered%20quitting%2C%20but%20I%20love%20writing%2C%20and%20I%20have%20never%20been%20the%20type%20to%20give%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20still%20looking%20for%20a%20full-time%20writing%20job%20in%20New%20York%2C%20but%20I'm%20learning%20not%20to%20let%20it%20define%20my%20entire%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20such%20a%20strong%20believer%20that%20life%20happens%20for%20a%20reason.%20Maybe%20living%20in%20Santa%20Clarita%20again%20is%20teaching%20me%20lessons%20I%20need%20before%20I%20return%20to%20the%20city%20I%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELiz%20Lindain%20is%20a%20freelance%20entertainment%20journalist%20based%20in%20Southern%20California.%20Connect%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fliz-allison-lindain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Flizlindain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Flizlindain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%2