upreme%20Court's%20decision%20on%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20trade%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%206-3%20decision%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20court%20ruled%20that%20imposing%20most%20of%20Trump's%20tariffs%20exceeded%20his%20authority%20under%20a%201970s%20law.%20The%20ruling%20is%20a%20hefty%20blow%20to%20the%20policies%20he%20put%20in%20place%20against%20foreign%20countries%2C%20which%20companies%20have%20had%20to%20reckon%20with%20for%20nearly%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWatch%20dealers%20have%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20they%20and%20their%20shoppers%20stand%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20ruling.%20Pre-owned%20watch%20retailer%20SwissWatchExpo%20CEO%20Eugene%20Tutunikov%20said%20it%20would%20likely%20lead%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpre-owned-watch-sales-bobs-watches-increase-as-tariffs-loom-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elower%20pre-owned%20watch%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20next%20six%20months%20%E2%80%94%20he%20expects%20declines%20of%202%25%20to%203%25.%20Without%20tariffs%20looming%20overhead%2C%20the%20market%20is%20poised%20to%20snap%20back%20faster%20than%20retail%20prices%20as%20sellers%20set%20their%20prices%20and%20buyers%20take%20the%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSupply%20will%20loosen%20up%2C%20and%20purchasing%20power%20goes%20right%20back%20to%20the%20collector%20where%20it%20belongs%2C%26quot%3B%20Tutunikov%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20break%20from%20tariffs%20would%20make%20the%20entry%20point%20for%20luxury%20watch%20collecting%20more%20accessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECue%20the%20celebrations%20among%20Swiss%20watch%20lovers%20who've%20been%20caught%20in%20a%20storm%20of%20retail%20price%20increases%20from%20leading%20brands%20like%20Rolex%20over%20the%20past%20year.%20Supply%20chain%20constraints%20also%20made%20it%20harder%20to%20do%20business%20in%20the%20secondhand%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frolex-models-drove-pre-owned-watch-sales-as-tariffs-loomed-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETariff%20tensions%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20Switzerland%20and%20the%20US%20have%20been%20up%20and%20down%20since%20Trump's%20Liberation%20Day.%20US%20imports%20of%20Swiss%20goods%20faced%20a%20baseline%20tariff%20of%2010%25%20from%20April%202025%20until%20Trump%20eventually%20raised%20it%20to%2039%25%2C%20sending%20shockwaves%20through%20the%20watch%20industry.%20The%20two%20countries%20continued%20negotiations%20until%20Trump%20agreed%20to%20lower%20the%20rate%20to%2015%25%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-says-agreed-lower-tariffs-swiss-imports-rolex-davos-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Espeaking%20with%20Rolex%20and%20other%20Swiss%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-reaction-supreme-court-scotus-tariff-ruling-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eclapped%20back%20at%20the%20nation's%20highest%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20its%20Friday%20ruling%2C%20saying%20he'd%20find%20alternative%20ways%20to%20keep%20his%20trade%20agenda%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Supreme%20Court%20did%20not%20overrule%20tariffs.%20They%20merely%20overruled%20a%20particular%20use%20of%20IEPPA%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%2C%20citing%20the%20law%20referenced%20in%20the%20court's%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20move%20is%20still%20a%20win%20in%20the%20books%20of%20watch%20dealers%20who've%20said%20the%20decision%20would%20allow%20pricing%20in%20the%20pre-owned%20market%20to%20return%20to%20being%20based%20on%20value%20and%20demand%20rather%20than%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20are%20indeed%20lifted%2C%20we%20expect%20it%20would%20meaningfully%20improve%20sentiment%20across%20the%20industry%2C%20increase%20access%20to%20important%20pieces%2C%20and%20ultimately%20benefit%20collectors%2C%20retailers%2C%20and%20brands%20alike%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Joshua%20Ganjei%2C%20CEO%20of%20European%20Watch%20Company%2C%20which%20sells%20pre-owned%20and%20vintage%20watches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwatch-collectors-could-gain-from-trumps-tariff-loss-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771671481000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6998aebeefb52c8bd0de9367%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwatch-collectors-could-gain-from-trumps-tariff-loss-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20watch%20world%20is%20rejoicing%20over%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20ruling%20on%20Trump's%20tariffs%20as%20dealers%20say%20the%20prices%20of%20pre-owned%20Swiss%20watches%20could%20dip.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhart%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Hart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwatch-collectors-could-gain-from-trumps-tariff-loss-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IND%20vs%20SA%3A%20Ahmedabad%20stadium%20stats%2C%20h2h%2C%20weather%20forecast%20and%20more%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771671392000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-128642118%2Cimgsize-205198.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-mens-t20-world-cup%2Findia-vs-south-africa-super-8s-t20-world-cup-2026-ahmedabad-stadium-stats-head-to-head-weather-forecast-and-more%2Farticleshow%2F128641338.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20will%20start%20their%20Super%208%20campaign%20against%20South%20Africa%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20with%20coach%20Morne%20Morkel%20confident%20batters%20will%20soon%20improve%20against%20spin.%20He%20believes%20India%20can%20post%20big%20totals%20and%20defend%20them%20with%20strong%20bowling.%20Ahmedabad%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20hot%20and%20dry%2C%20favouring%20batting-first%20teams.%20India%20lead%20the%20T20%20head-to-head%2018%E2%80%9312.%20India%20also%20face%20Zimbabwe%20and%20West%20Indies%20next.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Here's%20who%20could%20benefit%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20decision%20on%20Trump's%20IEEPA%20tariffs%20and%20who%20could%20lose%20out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227462%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22FEBRUARY%2020%3A%20U.S.%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20speaks%20during%20a%20press%20briefing%20at%20the%20White%20House%20on%20February%2020%2C%202026%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%20The%20U.S.%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20February%2020%20ruled%20against%20Trump's%20use%20of%20emergency%20powers%20to%20implement%20international%20trade%20tariffs%2C%20a%20central%20portion%20of%20the%20administration's%20core%20economic%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6998fc7e2237a6a8f0cd97e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20that%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20IEEPA%20tariffs%20were%20illegal.%3Cp%3EChen%20Mengtong%2FChina%20News%20Service%2FVCG%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20rules%20that%20Trump's%20IEEPA%20tariffs%20are%20illegal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBusinesses%20are%20celebrating%20the%20SCOTUS%20ruling%2C%20but%20tariff%20refunds%20may%20pose%20a%20fresh%20challenge.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20federal%20government%20could%20be%20on%20the%20hook%20to%20refund%20%24129%20billion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration's%20cornerstone%20policy%20just%20suffered%20a%20major%20setback%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20not%20bad%20news%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%206-3%20decision%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-scotus-rules-trump-tariffs-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20ruled%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Friday%20morning%20that%20the%20president%20does%20not%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20impose%20tariffs%20using%20the%20International%20Emergency%20Economic%20Powers%20Act.%20Most%20of%20the%20tariffs%20Trump%20imposed%20in%202025%2C%20including%20the%20%26quot%3Breciprocal%26quot%3B%20tariffs%20and%20the%2010%25%20baseline%20duties%2C%20made%20under%20IEEPA%2C%20have%20now%20been%20ruled%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20consumers%20to%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20here%20is%20who%20will%20stand%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20SCOTUS%20ruling%2C%20and%20who%20loses%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dd08f97b-7270-4d8e-a26f-3aa4d1a6fae0%5C%22%3EThe%20winners%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c7b13cbd-b7bd-4660-9190-b9e524e1f8cc%5C%22%3ETrade%20lawyers%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBusinesses%2C%20large%20and%20small%2C%20that%20want%20to%20get%20tariff%20money%20back%20from%20the%20US%20government%20will%20need%20lawyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20made%20it%20clear%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20US%20government%20will%20not%20make%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariff-refund-process-how-works-court-international-trade-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eimmediate%20refunds%3C%2Fa%3E%20despite%20the%20ruling%20that%20the%20IEEPA%20tariffs%20are%20illegal.%20That%20is%20because%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20did%20not%20explicitly%20state%20that%20the%20administration%20needs%20to%20make%20refunds.%20The%20matter%20could%20%26quot%3Bend%20up%20in%20court%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20in%20his%20fiery%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoyce%20Adetutu%2C%20an%20international%20trade%20lawyer%20at%20Vinson%20%26amp%3B%20Elkins%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20a%20refund%20of%20this%20magnitude%20is%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20process%20will%20likely%20be%20%26quot%3Bdaunting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPreparing%20for%20refunds%2C%20potential%20litigation%2C%20and%20contract%20interpretations%20will%20likely%20be%20a%20heavy%20lift%20going%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20Adetutu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdetutu%20added%20that%20importers%20should%20immediately%20gather%20documentation%2C%20be%20ready%20to%20file%20protests%2C%20and%20plan%20for%20litigation%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERyan%20Petersen%2C%20CEO%20of%20Flexport%2C%20a%20global%20logistics%20company%2C%20wrote%20on%20X%20on%20Friday%20that%20international%20trade%20attorneys%20he%20spoke%20with%20could%20charge%20clients%2015%25%20of%20the%20tariff%20refund%20amount%20to%20help%20them%20claim%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226eb51155-0662-4868-83fd-9cb7429e7e3a%5C%22%3ETrump's%20political%20foes%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20lawmakers%20are%20now%20calling%20for%20Trump%20to%20hand%20out%20tariff%20refund%20checks%20to%20households.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDonald%20Trump%20should%20return%20that%20money%20immediately.%20He%20has%20an%20obligation%2C%26quot%3B%20California%20Gov.%20Gavin%20Newsom%20said%20on%20Friday.%20%26quot%3BHe%20took%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20from%20working%20folks%2C%20from%20the%20ag%20community%2C%20from%20small%20businesses%20for%20this%20vanity%20play%2C%20this%20illegal%20action%2C%20and%20he%20finally%20was%20held%20to%20account.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIllinois%20Gov.%20JB%20Pritzker%20sent%20Trump%20an%20%26quot%3Binvoice%26quot%3B%20letter%20to%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20behalf%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Illinois%2C%20I%20demand%20a%20refund%20of%20%241%2C700%20for%20every%20family%20in%20Illinois%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22daa150fb-0b21-4543-a801-624f2501c369%5C%22%3ELosers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229e373e74-ad98-4b09-82d1-121d72328b23%5C%22%3EThe%20US%20government%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20did%20the%20decision%20upend%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20Trump's%20economic%20agenda%2C%20but%20the%20federal%20government%20could%20be%20on%20the%20hook%20for%20a%20huge%20sum%20of%20money%20as%20US%20companies%20and%20importers%20fight%20to%20claw%20back%20the%20tariffs%20they%20paid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%2C%20as%20of%20December%2010%2C%202025%2C%20a%20total%20of%20over%2034%20million%20entries%20subject%20to%20IEEPA%20duties%20have%20been%20made%20by%20over%20301%2C000%20importers%2C%20amounting%20to%20around%20%24129%20billion%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-paid-almost-entirely-by-americans-german-study-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etariff%20revenue%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Committee%20for%20a%20Responsible%20Budget%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20tariff%20ruling%20will%20reduce%20revenues%20on%20net%20by%20%241.9%20trillion%20through%20Fiscal%20Year%202036%20and%20increase%20debt%20by%20%242.4%20trillion%20over%20the%20same%20period%2C%20assuming%20the%20tariffs%20are%20refunded%20without%20replacement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20has%20been%20abundantly%20clear%3A%20Tariffs%20are%20here%20to%20stay%2C%20and%20the%20America%20Last%20era%20of%20American%20workers%20being%20ripped%20off%20is%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20White%20House%20Spokesman%20Kush%20Desai%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20administration%20would%20find%20other%20avenues%20for%20Trump's%20trade%20and%20economic%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEither%20way%2C%20tariffs%20and%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20ruling%20could%20complicate%20a%202026%20midterm%20election%20message%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20on%20affordability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d54cc189-df03-49d0-b466-c52bd773a0bd%5C%22%3EIt's%20complicated%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22012c1ad9-958f-4971-9b8e-cab863c7d096%5C%22%3EConsumers%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20households%20could%20see%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprices-food-coffee-gas-clothes-pets-rent-survey-inflation-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einflation%20and%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20ease%2C%20but%20it%20may%20not%20happen%20quickly%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20may%20not%20happen%20across%20all%20goods%2C%20depending%20on%20additional%20tariffs%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20Fed's%20Research%20and%20Statistics%20Group%2C%20along%20with%20research%20analyst%20Chris%20Flanagan%20and%20economist%20Sebastian%20Heise%2C%20found%20that%2094%25%20of%20tariffs%20were%20paid%20by%20domestic%20businesses%20and%20consumers%20in%20the%20first%20eight%20months%20of%202025.%20The%20Federal%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20St.%20Louis%20separately%20wrote%20in%20October%202025%20that%20tariffs%20are%20exerting%20%26quot%3Bmeasurable%20upward%20pressure%26quot%3B%20on%20consumer%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJosh%20Ketter%2C%20CEO%20of%20Spreetail%2C%20a%20top%20100%20US%20importer%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20there%20may%20not%20be%20immediate%20price%20cuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRetailers%20haven't%20passed%20on%20the%20full%20cost%20of%20tariffs%20to%20consumers%20over%20the%20past%20year%3B%20instead%2C%20they've%20seen%20their%20margins%20squeezed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ketter.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20first%20priority%20for%20tariff%20refunds%20will%20be%20to%20make%20themselves%20financially%20whole%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20tariffs%20are%20not%20completely%20going%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%2C%20issued%20under%20other%20statutes%2C%20remain%2C%20and%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20Friday%20signed%20a%20proclamation%20imposing%2010%25%20tariffs%20for%20150%20days%2C%20starting%20on%20February%2024%2C%20under%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariff-law-options-supreme-court-decision-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESection%20122%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Trade%20Act%20of%201974.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20exemptions%20for%20certain%20categories%2C%20according%20to%20the%20proclamation%2C%20including%20critical%20minerals%20and%20some%20agricultural%20products%2C%20and%20prices%20could%20come%20down%20for%20exempt%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b70e23ca-5435-4c55-8dd4-150bec081255%5C%22%3EBusinesses%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESmall%20businesses%20that%20led%20the%20charge%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-scotus-rules-trump-tariffs-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIEEPA%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20celebrating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20impossible%20to%20describe%20the%20feeling%20of%20elation%2C%20of%20seeing%20that%20yes%2C%20we%20were%20right%20and%20the%20court%20agrees%20with%20us%2C%20and%20a%20feeling%20that%20justice%20prevailed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flead-plaintiff-in-case-against-trumps-tariffs-wine-improting-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVictor%20Schwartz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20lead%20plaintiff%20in%20the%20case%20against%20tariffs%20and%20the%20owner%20of%20VOS%20Selections%2C%20in%20a%20media%20event%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVOS%20Selections%20is%20a%20wine-importing%20company%20based%20in%20New%20York%20that%20specializes%20in%20European%20specialty%20wines.%20For%20now%2C%20the%20company%20will%20have%20more%20cash%20flow%20from%20no%20longer%20needing%20to%20pay%20tariffs%20upfront%20before%20a%20single%20bottle%20of%20wine%20even%20sells.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchwartz%20said%20the%20amount%20of%20tariffs%20his%20company%20has%20paid%20so%20far%20sits%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Blow%20six%20figures%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20doesn't%20know%20when%20he%20could%20see%20a%20refund.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHong%2C%20global%20lead%20of%20Kearney%20Foresight%2C%20however%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20companies%20should%20not%20assume%20rapid%20balance-sheet%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20reimbursement%20process%20is%20likely%20to%20move%20through%20the%20customs%20liquidation%20system%20and%20would%20be%20administratively%20slow%2C%20burdensome%2C%20and%20likely%20drawn%20out%20over%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELarge%20global%20companies%2C%20including%20Costco%2C%20Toyota%2C%20and%20Chinese%20EV%20maker%20BYD%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthere-top-global-companies-have-sued-trump-for-tariff-refunds-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efiled%20suits%20even%20before%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20decision%20to%20maintain%20their%20right%20to%20refunds.%20Some%20of%20the%20tariffs%20they%20have%20paid%20have%20already%20been%20processed%20through%20customs%2C%20a%20process%20called%20%26quot%3Bliquidation%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20getting%20the%20money%20back%20could%20require%20extensive%20litigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwinner-and-losers-of-scotus-decision-strike-down-ieepa-tariffs-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771671302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6998fc94156648bc16a8a6e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwinner-and-losers-of-scotus-decision-strike-down-ieepa-tariffs-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Consumers%2C%20small%20businesses%2C%20and%20trade%20lawyers%20could%20all%20benefit%20in%20some%20way%20from%20the%20SCOTUS%20decision%20against%20IEEPA%20tariffs%2C%20but%20it's%20complicated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22katherineli%40insider.com%20(Katherine%20Li)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwinner-and-losers-of-scotus-decision-strike-down-ieepa-tariffs-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supplements%20are%20the%20new%20obsession%2C%20even%20as%20doctors%20stay%20wary.%20I%20went%20inside%20one%20of%20the%20industry's%20biggest%20factories.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226446%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kenzie%20Goer%20walks%20through%20the%20distribution%20area%20of%20Thorne's%20warehouse%20and%20shares%20products%2C%20Friday%2C%20September%205%2C%202025%2C%20in%20Summerville.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69864015d3c7faef0ecdce92%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224375%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKenzie%20Goer%2C%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20planning%20and%20distribution%20at%20Thorne%2C%20showed%20us%20around%20the%20supplement%20company's%20newest%20warehouse%20in%20Summerville%2C%20South%20Carolina.%3Cp%3EHenry%20Taylor%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20I%20stepped%20inside%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fsupplements%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esupplement%3C%2Fa%3E%20factory%2C%20the%20sweet%20smell%20of%20red%20berries%20filled%20the%20air.%20It%20reminded%20me%20of%20being%20a%20kid%20and%20gorging%20on%20chewable%20multivitamins%20%E2%80%94%20a%20not-quite-natural%20%26quot%3Bmixed%20berry%26quot%3B%20scent%20that%20was%20both%20nostalgic%20and%20vaguely%20medicinal.%20As%20factory%20tour%20smells%20go%2C%20it%20could%20have%20been%20much%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20Thorne's%20headquarters%2C%20raw%20materials%20from%20around%20the%20world%20were%20arriving%20by%20the%20pallet.%20Under%20the%20neon%20lights%20of%20a%20giant%2C%20temperature-controlled%20warehouse%20outside%20Charleston%2C%20South%20Carolina%2C%20forklifts%20hummed%20and%20beeped%20as%20they%20stacked%20ingredients%20on%20towering%20shelves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20here%2C%20it's%20always%2070%20degrees%20and%20dialed%20in%20to%20a%20moderate%2060%25%20humidity%20level.%20The%20relief%20stepping%20in%20from%20the%20muggy%20southern%20heat%20outside%20was%20immediate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20in%20factory%20world%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Claire%20Critchell%20explains%20steps%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20process%20for%20Thorne%20supplement%20products%2C%20Friday%2C%20September%205%2C%202025%2C%20in%20Summerville.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698640aae1ba468a96ab9633%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EClaire%20Critchell%2C%20Thorne's%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20operations%2C%20shows%20us%20the%20encapsulation%20and%20bottling%20area%20where%20workers%20in%20full-body%20suits%20prepare%20products.%3Cp%3EHenry%20Taylor%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samples%20are%20stored%20inside%20a%20tray%20at%20the%20labs%20of%20Thorne's%20manufacturing%20facility%2C%20Friday%2C%20September%205%2C%202025%2C%20in%20Summerville.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69864286d3c7faef0ecdcf47%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStudies%20suggest%20that%20most%20supplements%20don't%20contain%20what's%20advertised%20on%20the%20label.%20At%20Thorne%2C%20we%20saw%20some%20samples%20being%20tested%20for%20potency.%3Cp%3EHenry%20Taylor%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20saw%20pallets%20of%20creatine%20monohydrate%2C%20long%20popular%20with%20bodybuilders%20for%20improving%20strength%2C%20speed%2C%20and%20recovery.%20Indian%20barberry%20%E2%80%94%20the%20source%20of%20berberine%2C%20which%20influencers%20sometimes%20call%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-berberine-this-supplement-isnt-natures-ozempic-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enature's%20Ozempic%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20was%20also%20being%20stocked.%20(It's%20not%20actually%20comparable%20to%20GLP-1%20drugs.)%20Flavoring%20agents%20destined%20to%20become%20mango%20limeade%20or%20blood%20orange%20electrolytes%20sat%20quarantined%20until%20they%20could%20be%20cleared%20for%20use.%20Workers%20in%20full-body%20suits%20moved%20between%20sealed%20mixing%20rooms%20where%20air%20pressure%20kept%20outside%20dust%20out.%20No%20perfume.%20No%20open-toed%20shoes.%20No%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFacilities%20like%20this%20one%20are%20increasingly%20common.%20The%20supplement%20industry%20has%20been%20quietly%20expanding%20its%20manufacturing%20footprint%20across%20the%20US%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshould-i-take-supplements-scientist-benefits-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eracing%20to%20meet%20demand%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20surged%20during%20the%20pandemic%20and%20has%20never%20slowed.%20Thorne's%20newest%20warehouse%2C%20which%20opened%20in%202023%20and%20doubled%20its%20manufacturing%20capacity%20to%20549%2C000%20square%20feet%20%E2%80%94%20about%20six%20football%20fields%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20monument%20to%20the%20supplement%20boom.%20The%20company%20poured%20%2435%20million%20into%20expansion%20after%20moving%20from%20a%20small-town%20Idaho%20factory%20to%20this%20suburban%20South%20Carolina%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumers%20are%20clamoring%20for%20supplements%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwomens-morning-routines-for-success-productivity-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edaily%20powders%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20fueled%20by%20influencers%2C%20personalized%20medicine%2C%20and%20a%20fast-growing%20online%20market%20for%20both%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feli-lilly-retatrutide-gray-market-in-fitness-circles-before-launch-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epeptides%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20supplements%20that's%20racing%20ahead%20of%20regulation%20and%20bypassing%20doctors'%20recommendations.%20The%20docto