ttles%20for%20packaging%20sit%20in%20a%20large%20bucket%20on%20the%20manufacturing%20line%2C%20Friday%2C%20September%205%2C%202025%2C%20in%20Summerville.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69864227d3c7faef0ecdcf28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECzap%20said%20many%20supplements%20aren't%20formulated%20properly%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20many%20don't%20get%20absorbed%20by%20the%20body.%3Cp%3EHenry%20Taylor%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20same%20company%20that%20founder%20Al%20Czap%20started%20in%201984.%20A%20former%20supplement%20salesman%2C%20he%20started%20the%20company%20after%20seeing%20the%20poor%20state%20of%20industry%20manufacturing%20standards.%20He%20thought%20there%20were%20too%20many%20additives%2C%20too%20many%20hidden%20ingredients%2C%20too%20much%20messy%20manufacturing%2C%20creating%20ineffective%2C%20or%20worse%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-doctors-dangers-of-taking-multiple-supplements-less-is-more-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edangerous%20products%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20he%20started%20to%20make%20his%20own.%20He%20built%20a%20successful%20business%20selling%20directly%20to%20doctors%2C%20bypassing%20stores%20and%20advertising%20entirely%2C%20establishing%20a%20brand%20based%20on%20quality%20and%20clean%20manufacturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20dealing%20with%20physicians%20who%20knew%20nutritional%20medicine%2C%20and%20they%20would%20bring%20the%20patient%20in%2C%20and%20they%20would%20look%20at%20their%20blood%20pattern.%20They%20would%20look%20at%20doing%20urinalysis.%20They%20would%20get%20the%20symptoms%2C%20and%20they%20would%20say%2C%20'Alright%2C%20I've%20had%20success%20with%20this%20product%2C%20and%20I%20would%20like%20you%20to%20take%20this%20product%2C'%26quot%3B%20Czap%20told%20me%20about%20the%20early%20days%20of%20Thorne.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECzap%20stepped%20down%20as%20CEO%20in%202010%2C%20and%20after%20that%2C%20the%20company%20went%20through%20a%20period%20of%20rapid%20commercialization%20and%20expansion%2C%20first%20with%20Czap%20remaining%20as%20a%20shareholder%20and%20consultant%2C%20and%20later%20with%20private%20equity%20firm%20L%20Catterton%20taking%20full%20control.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20Thorne%20developed%20flashier%20packaging%2C%20built%20an%20online%20presence%2C%20and%20launched%20consumer-facing%20blogs%20before%20starting%20to%20sell%20directly%20to%20consumers%20in%202018.%20They%20didn't%20know%20it%20then%2C%20but%20soon%20they'd%20be%20in%20prime%20position%20to%20ship%20out%20supplements%20directly%20to%20consumers%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20A%20highly%20absorbable%20form%20of%20zinc%2C%20called%20zinc%20picolinate%2C%20was%20Thorne's%20big%20seller%20during%20lockdown%2C%20as%20shoppers%20scrambled%20to%20pick%20up%20anything%20that%20might%20boost%20their%20immunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20biggest%20names%20in%20the%20wellness%20space%2C%20including%20controversial%20wellness%20giants%20Andrew%20Huberman%20and%20Peter%20Attia%2C%20have%20mentioned%20Thorne%20by%20name%2C%20noting%20the%20brand's%20reputation%20for%20quality%2C%20even%20though%20Thorne%20is%20far%20from%20the%20largest%20player%20in%20the%20game.%20It's%20dwarfed%20by%20supplement%20giants%20including%20Nature%20Made%2C%20Nature's%20Bounty%2C%20Nestl%C3%A9's%20Garden%20of%20Life%2C%20and%20Bayer's%20One%20A%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f4bdc127-70ad-4515-85bc-3a7f5852d625%5C%22%3EQuality%20varies%20in%20a%20lightly%20regulated%20market%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInfluencer%20endorsements%20are%20big%2C%20especially%20in%20supplements%2C%20where%20it's%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20know%20exactly%20what%20you're%20getting.%20Unlike%20pharmaceuticals%2C%20supplements%20are%20not%20approved%20by%20the%20FDA%20before%20they%20hit%20shelves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20a%201994%20law%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-supplement-experts-tips-for-buying-safe-products-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emanufacturers%20are%20largely%20responsible%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20ensuring%20their%20own%20products%20are%20safe%20and%20accurately%20labeled.%20The%20FDA%20does%20show%20up%20to%20inspect%20supplement%20makers%20%E2%80%94%20Thorne%20is%20quick%20to%20point%20this%20out%20%E2%80%94%20but%20those%20inspections%20aren't%20mandatory%20or%20regularly%20scheduled%2C%20they're%20mere%20retroactive%20checks%20on%20manufacturing%20and%20labeling.%20That%20regulatory%20gap%20has%20allowed%20innovation%20to%20flourish.%20It%20has%20also%20led%20to%20mislabeling%2C%20contamination%2C%20and%20exaggerated%20claims%20across%20the%20industry.%20Sometimes%2C%20the%20FDA%20only%20shows%20up%20after%20people%20complain%20about%20a%20brand%20or%20get%20sick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20Thorne%20says%20it's%20eager%20to%20differentiate%20itself.%20Every%20product%20at%20the%20factory%20undergoes%20four%20rounds%20of%20testing%2C%20they%20say%20again%20and%20again.%20During%20my%20tour%2C%20I%20see%20miniature%20metal%20detectors%20screening%20raw%20materials%20and%20finished%20capsules%20coming%20off%20the%20line%2C%20checking%20repeatedly%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-protect-kids-from-heavy-metals-in-baby-foods-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eheavy%20metals%3C%2Fa%3E%20inside%20the%20pills.%20Refrigerators%20and%20heaters%20churn%20with%20finished%20pill%20bottles%20inside%2C%20testing%20to%20ensure%20the%20finished%20products%20remain%20stable%20across%20various%20climates.%20I'm%20introduced%20to%20lab%20workers%20in%20white%20coats%20and%20goggles%20who%20are%20uncapping%20products%20and%20spooning%20out%20scoops%20of%20powder%20to%20test%20for%20microbial%20contamination%20and%20potency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20times%2C%20it%20feels%20excessive%2C%20but%20in%20an%20industry%20where%20trust%20is%20fragile%2C%20that%20redundancy%20is%20part%20of%20the%20brand%20ethos%2C%20Price%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225347%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20machine%20repeatedly%20shakes%20bottles%20back%20and%20forth%20inside%20the%20labs%20at%20Thorne's%20manufacturing%20facility%2C%20Friday%2C%20September%205%2C%202025%2C%20in%20Summerville.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698642a6e1ba468a96ab96cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223505%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESamples%20are%20shaken%20before%20testing.%3Cp%3EHenry%20Taylor%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Autumn%20Mitchell%20holds%20up%20a%20testing%20tray%20with%20a%20culture%20on%20it%20inside%20the%20Thorne%20facility's%20micro%20lab%2C%20Friday%2C%20September%205%2C%202025%2C%20in%20Summerville.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69864412a645d1188188e0a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELab%20workers%20check%20to%20ensure%20that%20harmful%20bacteria%2C%20such%20as%20mold%2C%20can't%20grow%20on%20the%20supplements.%3Cp%3EHenry%20Taylor%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20position%20as%20a%20premium%20brand%2C%20but%20to%20maintain%20that%20reputation%2C%20we're%20very%20strict%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20we%20do%20%5Btest%5D%20repeatedly%20just%20draws%20the%20probability%20of%20us%20having%20a%20negative%20to%20be%20very%2C%20very%20small.%20It's%20a%20trade-off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20about%20his%20thoughts%20on%20the%20company's%20current%20standards%2C%20Czap%20is%20pleased%20that%20quality%20control%20remains%20paramount.%20%26quot%3BKudos%20to%20them%20because%20they%20didn't%20screw%20it%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me%2C%20adding%20he%20still%20gets%20his%20own%20supplements%20from%20Thorne.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIt%20seems%20customers%20are%20taking%20notice%2C%20too.%20One%20of%20Thorne's%20most%20popular%20products%2C%20creatine%2C%20had%20more%20than%2012%2C700%205-star%20reviews%20on%20Amazon%20at%20the%20time%20of%20publication%2C%20with%20hundreds%20of%20customers%20commenting%20on%20its%20high%20quality%20and%20dissolvability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22227064c2-473a-4749-8520-81dabf072d71%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20plenty%20of%20pitfalls%2C%20even%20with%20'safe'%20products%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20a%20product%20is%20safe%2C%20some%20consumers%20will%20overdo%20it.%20A%20woman%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20seeking%20inflammation%20and%20joint%20pain%20relief%2C%20recently%20suffered%20liver%20damage%20after%20she%20followed%20the%20advice%20of%20a%20person%20who%20said%20they%20were%20a%20doctor%20on%20social%20media%20and%20recommended%20a%20monster%2010x%20dose%20of%20turmeric%20every%20day.%20(It's%20not%20clear%20what%20brand%20of%20turmeric%20supplement%20she%20was%20using.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20consumer%20misuse%2C%20numerous%20studies%20show%20that%20most%20supplements%20don't%20accurately%20contain%20what%20they%20say%20on%20the%20label.%20Certain%20additives%20deemed%20%26quot%3Bincidental%26quot%3B%20may%20not%20be%20listed%20at%20all.%20The%20FDA%20has%20even%20found%20prescription%20drugs%20like%20blood%20thinners%2C%20typically%20used%20to%20help%20prevent%20strokes%20and%20heart%20attacks%2C%20and%20anticonvulsants%2C%20prescribed%20for%20seizures%20and%20neuropathic%20pain%2C%20masquerading%20as%20%26quot%3Bsupplements.%26quot%3B%20It's%20a%20mess.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20and%20longevity%20experts%20I've%20spoken%20with%20aren't%20categorically%20opposed%20to%20supplements.%20Still%2C%20many%20resent%20what%20a%20minefield%20it%20can%20be%20picking%20out%20the%20right%20products%20for%20the%20right%20person.%20Most%20agree%20that%20consumers%20shouldn't%20do%20this%20on%20their%20own%2C%20with%20no%20guardrails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20struggle%20with%20the%20supplement%20industry%2C%20not%20because%20I%20don't%20believe%20that%20some%20supplements%20have%20value%2C%20some%20certainly%20do%2C%20but%20I%20just%20feel%20like%20the%20incentive%20structures%20are%20all%20geared%20toward%20forcing%20companies%2C%20individuals%2C%20people%20in%20that%20industry%20who%20are%20marketing%20supplements%20to%20be%20dishonest%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Matt%20Kaeberlein%2C%20a%20scientist%20who%20studies%20the%20biological%20mechanisms%20of%20aging%2C%20and%20who%20recently%20cofounded%20Optispan%2C%20a%20longevity%20healthcare%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Haleem%20Mohammed%2C%20the%20Chief%20Medical%20Officer%20at%20Gameday%20Men's%20Health%2C%20where%20he%20focuses%20on%20hormonal%20health%2C%20said%20he%20often%20sees%20patients%20get%20%26quot%3Bburned%26quot%3B%20by%20inflated%20influencer%20claims%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20supplement%20brands%20and%20supplement%20shillers%20and%20influencers%20can%20make%20any%20sort%20of%20claims%20they%20want%2C%20whether%20it's%20performance%2C%20fat%20loss%2C%20libido%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20formulating%2C%20testing%2C%20verifying%20anything.%20They're%20out%20there%20cherry-picking%20studies.%20They're%20using%20animal%20data%20that's%20stretched%20into%20human%20claims.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22265d7372-f092-4d69-ad4f-6a455a43538b%5C%22%3ECreatine%2C%20testosterone%2C%20anti-inflammatories%2C%20and%20gut%20health%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20one%20supplement%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20that's%20now%20a%20bestseller%20across%20demographics.%20Inside%20Thorne's%20facility%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcreatine-most-effective-fitness-supplement-science-burn-fat-build-muscle-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecreatine%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20everywhere.%20Arriving%20by%20the%20pallet%20and%20showing%20up%20in%20cart%20after%20cart%2C%20being%20prepared%20to%20ship%20to%20a%20customer's%20doorstep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCreatine%20is%20the%20overnight%20sensation%2C%20even%20though%20it's%20been%20around%20forever%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ken%20Rowe%2C%20Thorne's%20chief%20R%26amp%3BD%20officer%2C%20and%20a%20former%20VP%20at%20Nestl%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20staple%20in%20gym%20lockers%2C%20it's%20now%20gaining%20steam%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcreatine-demand-soars-muscle-fat-loss-and-brain-power-benefits-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elongevity%20aid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20cognitive%20enhancer%2C%20and%20everyday%20health%20hack.%20It's%20one%20of%20the%20most%20well-studied%20supplements%2C%20with%20decades%20of%20research%20%E2%80%94%20something%20supplement%20proponents%2C%20like%20Price%2C%20are%20keen%20to%20mention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20some%20evidence%20now%20that%205%20grams%20kind%20of%20saturates%20up%20your%20muscles%2C%20but%20if%20you%20go%20to%2010%20grams%2C%20there's%20this%20notion%20that%20some%20of%20that%20overflow%20actually%20goes%20into%20the%20brain%2C%26quot%3B%20Price%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20are%20especially%20thrilled%20by%20a%2020-person%20study%20with%20no%20placebo%20arm.%20It%20was%20designed%20to%20test%20safety%2C%20not%20efficacy%2C%20though%20it%20showed%20marginal%20benefits%20that%20still%20need%20confirmation%20in%20larger%2C%20placebo-controlled%20trials.%20Already%2C%20word%20has%20traveled%20that%20it%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20looking%20at%20an%20article%20online%20right%20now%3A%20'Creatine%20shows%20potential%20to%20boost%20cognition.'%20That's%20not%20what%20they%20were%20saying%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Nathaniel%20Chin%2C%20medical%20director%20for%20the%20Wisconsin%20Alzheimer's%20Disease%20Research%20Center%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20were%20just%20saying%2C%20'This%20is%20feasible.%20People%20could%20take%20this.%20We%20should%20study%20this.%20We%20should%20see%20if%20this%20helps%20people%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C'%20which%20I'm%20excited%20about.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Raw%20materials%20for%20manufacturing%20Thorne%20supplements%20sit%20on%20shelves%20inside%20the%20warehouse%20of%20the%20manufacturing%20facility%2C%20Friday%2C%20September%205%2C%202025%2C%20in%20Summerville.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69864075d3c7faef0ecdcea6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERaw%20materials%2C%20including%20creatine%20monohydrate%20and%20Indian%20barberry%2C%20are%20sourced%20from%20around%20the%20world%20and%20delivered%20to%20Thorne.%3Cp%3EHenry%20Taylor%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225260%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20worker%20measures%20out%20material%20to%20be%20packaged%20into%20a%20bottle%20inside%20the%20Thorne%20manufacturing%20facility's%20labs%2C%20Friday%2C%20September%205%2C%202025%2C%20in%20Summerville.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698642dfe1ba468a96ab96e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223507%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFinished%20products%20are%20tested%20for%20both%20purity%20and%20potency.%3Cp%3EHenry%20Taylor%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENearby%2C%20in%20Thorne's%20testing%20labs%2C%20new%20flavors%20and%20formulations%20are%20already%20in%20development.%20Before%20we%20can%20lift%20the%20camera%20to%20take%20photos%2C%20workers%20quickly%20flip%20the%20labels%20on%20jars%20so%20we%20can't%20see%20the%20names%20of%20these%20not-yet-for-sale%20products%2C%20including%20two%20flavored%20versions%20of%20Thorne's%20creatine%20that%20it%20has%20since%20released%3A%20strawberry%20and%20pineapple-orange.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreatine%20is%20the%20industry%20standout%20star%20for%20now%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20forecasted%20compound%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%20around%2020-30%25%20in%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20not%20the%20only%20one.%20Women's%20health%2C%20gut%20health%2C%20and%20sports%20performance%20are%20Thorne's%20biggest%20categories%2C%20Rowe%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMagnesium%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvegetarians-fish-or-meat-for-brain-health-blue-zone-doctor-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efish%20oil%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20curcumin%20(the%20anti-inflammatory%20compound%20in%20turmeric)%2C%20prenatal%20vitamins%2C%20CoQ10%2C%20they%20are%20all%20here%2C%20buoyed%20by%20TikTok%20trends%2C%20podcast%20endorsements%2C%20and%20a%20broad%20obsession%20with%20longevity%20and%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20new%20%26quot%3Badvanced%20testosterone%20support%26quot%3B%20product%20made%20with%20ashwaganda%2C%20jumping%20into%20the%20hype%20around%20hormone%20health.%20%26quot%3BEven%20if%20people%20come%20in%20for%20creatine%2C%20then%20they%20find%20something%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20Rowe%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22083115be-e466-4d79-9da0-c7d4af783270%5C%22%3EDoctors%20are%20struggling%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20this%20innovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDoctors%20fear%20many%20patients%20are%20overdoing%20it%20in%20this%20DIY-your-stack%20world.%20There's%20little%20concern%20for%20how%20these%20ingredients%20might%20interact%20with%20or%20counteract%20one%20another%2C%20or%20a%20prescription%20medication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELongevity%20experts%20and%20medical%20professionals%20recommend%20a%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-doctors-dangers-of-taking-multiple-supplements-less-is-more-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etargeted%20approach%20to%20supplementation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Skip%20the%20blends%20and%20green%20powders%2C%20they%20say.%20Test%20for%20what%20you're%20deficient%20in%2C%20then%20add%20in%20supplements%20slowly%2C%20discuss%20your%20progress%20with%20your%20doctor%2C%20retest%2C