ss%20families.%20Despite%20a%20major%20setback%20in%202011%2C%20Agarwal%20made%20a%20powerful%20comeback%20with%20V2%20Retail%2C%20solidifying%20his%20status%20as%20a%20retail%20icon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22PRIYA%20SRIVASTAVA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Flife-style%2Fpeople%2Fhow-a-polio-survivor-from-a-humble-family-created-a-brand-worth-6500-crore-the-extraordinary-story-of-ram-chandra-agarwal%2Farticleshow%2F128641321.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20American%20family%20spent%20%241%2C330%20on%20a%20full%20day%20of%20luxury%20medical%20care%20in%20Turkey.%20Now%20they%20want%20to%20leave%20the%20US%20for%20good.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221351%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cara%20West%20and%20her%20family%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69972b0ff8731049f3af6406%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221013%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECara%20West%20and%20her%20family%20saved%20money%20through%20medical%20tourism.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20Courtesy%20of%20Cara%20West%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECara%20West%2C%2034%2C%20often%20seeks%20medical%20care%20abroad%20due%20to%20high%20prices%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20longtime%20Texas%20resident%20has%20sought%20care%20in%20Greece%2C%20Turkey%2C%20and%20Portugal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20family%20is%20likely%20to%20move%20abroad%20permanently%2C%20in%20part%20due%20to%20America's%20high%20cost%20of%20living.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECara%20West%20had%20never%20seen%20such%20a%20gorgeous%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2034-year-old%20is%20traveling%20the%20world%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20toddler%20and%20often%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmedical-tourism-boomer-cancer-treatment-save-money-medicare-insurance-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseeks%20medical%20care%20abroad%3C%2Fa%3E%20rather%20than%20in%20their%20hometown%20of%20Austin%2C%20Texas.%20Last%20summer%2C%20they%20flew%20to%20Istanbul%20for%20a%20primary%20care%20check-up.%20They%20stayed%20at%20a%20hotel%2C%20boarded%20the%20morning%20shuttle%20arranged%20by%20their%20medical%20tourism%20agency%2C%20and%20began%20a%20full-day%20itinerary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20family%20member%20received%20bloodwork%2C%20scans%2C%20an%20EKG%2C%20and%20doctor%20consultations%20over%20the%20next%20few%20hours.%20West's%20daughter%20even%20got%20her%20eyes%20checked.%20As%20a%20midday%20break%2C%20they%20ordered%20lunch%20at%20the%20hospital's%20restaurant%2C%20complete%20with%20a%20menu%20featuring%20items%20like%20veggie%20omelettes%20and%20raspberry%20cheesecake.%20It%20all%20felt%20%26quot%3Bluxurious.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20bill%20came%2C%20the%20total%20was%20%241%2C330%20before%20insurance%20%E2%80%94%20and%20West%20is%20still%20in%20shock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20this%20fear%20as%20an%20American%20because%20you%20know%20that%20medicine%20is%20so%20expensive%20and%20it's%20confusing%2C%26quot%3B%20West%20said.%20She%20estimates%20the%20same%20check-ups%20would%20have%20cost%20her%20family%20thousands%20more%20in%20the%20US%20and%20caused%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-cancer-work-career-impact-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emonths%20of%20insurance%20stress%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20been%20the%20biggest%20eye%20opener%2C%20this%20feeling%20of%20relief.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20healthcare%20or%20medical%20tourism%20story%20to%20tell%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aallisonkelly%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eallisonkelly%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20healthcare%20prices%20climb%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Americans%20are%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20cut%20costs.%20To%20avoid%20breaking%20the%20bank%2C%20more%20people%20are%20turning%20toward%20medical%20tourism.%20Some%20foreign%20hospitals%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20in%20places%20like%20Turkey%20%E2%80%94%20are%20even%20marketing%20themselves%20directly%20to%20American%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20on%20the%20phenomenon%20is%20limited%2C%20but%20the%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fyellow-book%2Fhcp%2Fhealth-care-abroad%2Fmedical-tourism.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emillions%20of%20Americans%3C%2Fa%3E%20seek%20healthcare%20abroad%20each%20year%2C%20most%20commonly%20in%20Mexico%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20the%20Caribbean.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebusinessresearchcompany.com%2Freport%2Finternational-health-insurance-global-market-report%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520international%2520health%2520insurance%2520market%2520size%2520has%2520grown%2520strongly%2520in%2Cavailability%2520of%2520international%2520insurance%2520providers.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarket%20for%20international%20health%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%20from%20nearly%20%2432%20billion%20in%202025%20to%20%2440%20billion%20in%202030%2C%20and%20North%20Americans%20account%20for%20the%20largest%20share.%20Patients%20travel%20for%20a%20range%20of%20services%2C%20including%20cosmetic%20surgeries%2C%20reproductive%20procedures%20like%20IVF%2C%20and%20cancer%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cara%20West%20and%20her%20daughter%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69972d83a645d11881899693%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWest%20and%20her%20daughter%20traveling%20in%20France%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Cara%20West%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220275bdf5-4bbb-42d5-9a0c-68dc8827dbbe%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWest%20plans%20to%20move%20abroad%20permanently%20%E2%80%94%20and%20cheaper%20healthcare%20sweetens%20the%20deal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWest%20and%20her%20husband%20first%20considered%20living%20abroad%20after%20the%20birth%20of%20their%20daughter%20in%202022.%20They%20were%20paying%20off%20expensive%20labor%20and%20delivery%20bills%2C%20and%20craving%20a%20more%20travel-oriented%20lifestyle.%20Temporarily%20relocating%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcities-abroad-lowest-cost-of-living-highest-quality-of-life-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elower-cost-of-living%20city%3C%2Fa%3E%20seemed%20like%20the%20perfect%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWest%20was%20working%20remotely%20for%20a%20startup%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20took%20a%20break%20from%20his%20job%20as%20a%20restaurant%20manager.%20With%20a%20combined%20six-figure%20income%2C%20they%20had%20been%20living%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-henrys-high-earners-not-rich-yet-income-renters-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enearly%20paycheck%20to%20paycheck%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Austin%20%E2%80%94%20but%20one%20salary%20was%20more%20than%20enough%20to%20comfortably%20afford%20life%20in%20Lisbon.%20They%20stayed%20for%20three%20months%20as%20part%20of%20a%20program%20for%20people%20interested%20in%20traveling%20and%20living%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20around%20this%20time%20that%20the%20family%20enrolled%20in%20an%20international%20healthcare%20plan.%20Their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femployers-cutting-back-employee-wellness-benefits-fitness-money-gyms-healthcare-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20employer-sponsored%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20become%20unaffordable%20and%20didn't%20meet%20their%20growing%20healthcare%20requirements%20while%20abroad%2C%20West%20said.%20They%20began%20regularly%20traveling%20overseas%20and%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20they%20could%20still%20easily%20fill%20prescriptions%20and%20visit%20urgent%20care%20when%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWest%20enrolled%20in%20the%20international%20healthcare%20plan%20Genki%2C%20which%20covers%20doctor%20visits%20and%20hospital%20stays%20for%20travelers%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftried-being-digital-nomad-portugal-not-easy-dream-expected-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edigital%20nomads%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20most%20countries.%20It%20costs%20%24657%20a%20month%20for%20the%20family%2C%20but%20she%20said%20she%20was%20paying%20nearly%20twice%20that%20in%20Texas%20with%20much%20higher%20deductibles.%20The%20deductible%20for%20international%20coverage%20is%20%241%2C000%2C%20though%20West%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20actually%20kind%20of%20hard%20to%20meet%20that%2C%20because%20the%20cost%20of%20medical%20care%20is%20actually%20very%20affordable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20Istanbul%20hospital%2C%20the%20family%20has%20received%20medical%20care%20in%20Portugal%20and%20Greece.%20West%20said%20all%20were%20covered%20by%20her%20international%20plan.%20She%20advised%20others%20interested%20in%20medical%20tourism%20to%20read%20reviews%2C%20reach%20out%20to%20hospitals%20directly%20with%20questions%2C%20and%20try%20a%20video%20chat%20with%20providers%20first%20before%20visiting%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cara%20Celeste%20and%20her%20husband%20in%20Santorini%2C%20Greece.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69972cf8a645d11881899675%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECara%20Celeste%20and%20her%20husband%20in%20Santorini%2C%20Greece.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Cara%20West%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20feel%20really%20uneasy%20because%20they%20think%2C%20'I'm%20going%20to%20a%20foreign%20country%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20get%20medical%20care.%20And%20what%20happens%20if%20something%20goes%20wrong%3F'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20it%20really%20is%20all%20about%20doing%20your%20research.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWest's%20family%20recently%20settled%20on%20the%20Greek%20island%2C%20Syros.%20They%20love%20the%20sunshine%20and%20close-knit%20community%2C%20and%20their%20move%20from%20Texas%20is%20likely%20permanent.%20Cheaper%20healthcare%20costs%20are%20a%20main%20reason%20for%20their%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20added%20bonus%2C%20West%20said%20the%20island%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floma-linda-blue-zone-longevity-secrets-of-seventh-day-adventists-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20Blue%20Zone%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20hopes%20it's%20good%20news%20for%20their%20longevity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20started%20learning%20from%20the%20older%20generation%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20the%20things%20that%20they%20do%2C%20and%20what%20they%20believe%20is%20keeping%20them%20healthy%20and%20young.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmedical-tourism-american-family-healthcare-turkey-saved-money-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771670581000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69972db0f8731049f3af6488%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmedical-tourism-american-family-healthcare-turkey-saved-money-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20rising%20US%20healthcare%20costs%2C%20Cara%20West%20found%20relief%20in%20medical%20tourism.%20Her%20family%20saved%20thousands%20getting%20tests%20and%20scans%20done%20in%20Turkey.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22allisonkelly%40businessinsider.com%20(Allie%20Kelly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmedical-tourism-american-family-healthcare-turkey-saved-money-2026-2%22%2C