rt's%20ruling%20on%20tariffs%20before%20issuing%20an%20official%20statement%2C%20with%20the%20commerce%20and%20external%20affairs%20ministries%20handling%20the%20response.%20Joshi%20also%20condemned%20the%20Indian%20Youth%20Congress's%20shirtless%20protest%20at%20the%20India%20AI%20Summit%20as%20shameful%20and%20disruptive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fgovt-will-study-union-minister-pralhad-joshi-on-us-supreme-court-ruling-striking-trump-tariffs%2Farticleshow%2F128641588.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%2026%25%20to%2050%25%20to%2010%25%3A%20A%20timeline%20of%20Donald%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20tariffs%20on%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771670348000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-128643122%2Cimgsize-107356.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Finternational-business%2Ffrom-26-to-50-to-10-a-timeline-of-donald-trumps-tariffs-on-india%2Farticleshow%2F128639394.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Corporate%20America's%20toughest%20job%3F%20Being%20COO%20during%20the%20tariff%20whiplash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20massive%20boats%20filled%20with%20shipping%20containers%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6998e658156648bc16a8a63c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStephen%20B.%20Morton%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20struck%20down%20much%20of%20Trump's%20tariffs%2C%20but%20Trump%20could%20try%20to%20impose%20levies%20in%20other%20ways.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECOOs%2C%20who%20are%20responsible%20for%20overseeing%20where%20companies%20build%20and%20source%20products%2C%20are%20in%20a%20tough%20spot.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20uncertainty%20and%20whiplash%20surrounding%20tariffs%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20frustrating%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20COO%20of%20an%20HVAC%20company.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFriday's%20tariff%20ruling%20has%20once%20again%20put%20America's%20supply-chain%20bosses%20in%20a%20bind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20striking%20down%20much%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20sweeping%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-scotus-rules-trump-tariffs-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etariff%20policy%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20created%20a%20fresh%20bout%20of%20uncertainty%20for%20chief%20operating%20officers%20and%20other%20leaders%20responsible%20for%20overseeing%20where%20companies%20build%20and%20source%20their%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20made%20strategic%20changes%20after%20the%20levies%20were%20announced%20last%20year%2C%20and%20the%20new%20ruling%20%E2%80%94%20plus%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-reaction-supreme-court-scotus-tariff-ruling-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump's%20strong%20reaction%20to%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20are%20now%20clouding%20their%20path%20forward.%20With%20the%20commander%20in%20chief%20fighting%20back%2C%20COOs%20must%20decide%20whether%20to%20proceed%20as%20if%20the%20court's%20decision%20is%20impenetrable%20or%20wait%20to%20see%20if%20the%20White%20House%20can%20successfully%20keep%20the%20tariffs%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTariffs%20are%20written%20in%20DC%2C%20and%20they're%20felt%20in%20the%20COO's%20inbox%2C%26quot%3B%20Jason%20Schloetzer%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20Georgetown's%20McDonough%20School%20of%20Business%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20an%20impossible%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226af8fdca-d9aa-435c-92f8-4429e6572e80%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDealing%20with%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3Edisruption%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20news%20conference%20held%20shortly%20after%20the%20ruling%2C%20Trump%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20court's%20justices%20who%20sided%20against%20him%2C%20saying%20they%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20ashamed%26quot%3B%20and%20accusing%20them%2C%20without%20evidence%2C%20of%20being%20%26quot%3Bswayed%20by%20foreign%20interests.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20said%20%26quot%3Balternatives%26quot%3B%20would%20be%20used%20to%20preserve%20his%20trade%20agenda%20and%20that%20he'd%20tap%20a%20separate%20authority%20to%20impose%20a%2010%25%20global%20tariff%20on%20top%20of%20existing%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20has%20been%20abundantly%20clear%3A%20Tariffs%20are%20here%20to%20stay%2C%20and%20the%20America%20Last%20era%20of%20American%20workers%20being%20ripped%20off%20is%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20White%20House%20Spokesman%20Kush%20Desai%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Administration%20will%20be%20pursuing%20other%20legal%20authorities%20to%20maintain%20President%20Trump's%20America%20First%20trade%20and%20economic%20agenda%20while%20continuing%20to%20implement%20a%20pro-growth%20agenda%20of%20tax%20cuts%2C%20deregulation%2C%20and%20energy%20abundance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20alternative%20was%20announced%20Friday%20night.%20Trump%20signed%20a%20proclamation%20that%20would%20implement%20a%20temporary%2010%25%20import%20surcharge%20for%20150%20days%2C%20starting%20on%20February%2024%2C%20under%20Section%20122%20of%20the%20Trade%20Act%20of%201974.%20The%20executive%20order%20also%20carved%20out%20exemptions%20for%20certain%20categories%2C%20including%20critical%20minerals%20and%20some%20agricultural%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20strategies%20Trump%20deploys%20will%20likely%20face%20legal%20and%20other%20hurdles%20that%20could%20take%20months%20to%20resolve%2C%20said%20Schloetzer.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20%26quot%3BCOOs%20will%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceos-pause-some-big-decisions-economy-trade-tariffs-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20the%20pause%20button%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20on%20decisions%20involving%20sourcing%2C%20factory%20locations%2C%20labor%2C%20and%20other%20expenses%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20companies%20are%20still%20grappling%20with%20the%20impact%20of%20actions%20they%20took%20last%20year%20to%20cope%20with%20Trump's%20tariff%20hikes%2C%20said%20Rob%20Lalka%2C%20who%20teaches%20entrepreneurship%20at%20Tulane%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20he%20said%20that%20some%20companies%20responded%20by%20raising%20prices%20on%20consumer%20goods%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20affected%20people's%20spending%20habits%20and%20opinions%20of%20those%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20disruption%20is%20something%20you%20can't%20reverse%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20with%20the%20fate%20of%20Trump's%20tariffs%20up%20in%20the%20air%2C%20COOs%20are%20experiencing%20the%20kind%20of%20whiplash%20that%20can%20be%20debilitating%2C%20said%20Lalka%2C%20especially%20for%20those%20at%20startups%20and%20small%20businesses%20with%20limited%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20the%20ones%20who%20are%20often%20working%20with%20the%20thinnest%20margins%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2263cb11d8-d606-49fe-a485-be3bcb08fd5e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EKeeping%20things%20humming%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFriday's%20ruling%20could%20also%20benefit%20companies%20financially%20through%20refunds.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20that%20the%20federal%20government%20illegally%20collected%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariff-refund-process-how-works-court-international-trade-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%20%24133%20billion%20in%20taxes%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20American%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20while%20business%20groups%20such%20as%20the%20US%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20and%20the%20National%20Retail%20Federation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-tariff-ruling-smart-reactions-trump-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehailed%20the%20court's%20decision%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Trump%20administration%20officials%20have%20suggested%20that%20issuing%20refunds%20would%20be%20a%20messy%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20the%20burden%20of%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20keep%20operations%20humming%20will%20fall%20largely%20on%20COOs%2C%20said%20Schloetzer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCEOs%20can%20always%20focus%20on%20talking%20about%20long-term%20strategies%2C%20and%20CFOs%20can%20focus%20on%20modeling%20what%20these%20things%20might%20mean%20for%20margins%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20COOs%20actually%20have%20to%20be%20the%20ones%20in%20the%20short-term%20that%20are%20delivering.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20in%20manufacturing%20have%20it%20particularly%20bad%2C%20he%20added%2C%20because%20such%20companies%20may%20need%20to%20move%20components%20across%20multiple%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20really%20is%20difficult%20to%20think%20through%20what%20the%20margin%20implications%20would%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Schloetzer.%20%26quot%3BThey've%20got%20to%20just%20be%20pulling%20their%20hair%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224d94e74d-99dd-490d-818b-dc2948353f74%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Back%20to%20where%20we%20were'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBrian%20Smith%2C%20COO%20of%20Omni%20Containment%20Systems%2C%20an%20Elgin%2C%20Illinois%2C%20manufacturer%20of%20HVAC%20cleaning%20systems%2C%20is%20feeling%20the%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20frustrating%20%E2%80%A6%20because%20of%20the%20journey%20that%20we%20just%20went%20on%20for%20one%20year%20in%20altering%20our%20import-export%20strategies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOmni%2C%20which%20imports%20goods%20from%20Spain%20and%20exports%20to%20Canada%2C%20lost%20sales%20last%20year%20due%20to%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20tariffs%2C%20Smith%20said.%20The%20company%20managed%2C%20however%2C%20and%20Smith%20said%20he%20thought%20%26quot%3Bthings%20had%20kind%20of%20stabilized%26quot%3B%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20take%20us%20right%20back%20to%20where%20we%20were%20in%20the%20first%20and%20second%20quarter%20of%20last%20year%2C%20which%20was%20complete%20uncertainty%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20added%20that%20it's%20hard%20to%20know%20how%20this%20will%20play%20out%20with%20suppliers%20and%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20have%20some%20conversations%20with%20our%20larger%20customers%20who%20buy%20multiple%20machines%20and%20discuss%20what%20influence%20this%20is%20going%20to%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20unknown%20he's%20wrestling%20with%20is%20whether%20a%20refund%20is%20headed%20Omni's%20way%20for%20the%20tariffs%20the%20company%20has%20paid%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20they%20going%20to%20do%20with%20all%20the%20money%20they%20collected%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Smith%20of%20the%20payments%20that%20the%20federal%20government%20illegally%20collected%20from%20US%20businesses%2C%20per%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20decision.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20could%20just%20answer%20that%20question%2C%20it%20would%20be%20helpful%20either%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoo-job-is-especially-challenging-with-tariff-uncertainty-scotus-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771670341000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6998e676efb52c8bd0de9c87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoo-job-is-especially-challenging-with-tariff-uncertainty-scotus-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22America's%20supply-chain%20bosses%20are%20experiencing%20a%20fresh%20bout%20of%20uncertainty%20after%20Friday's%20tariff%20ruling%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sneedleman%40businessinsider.com%20(Sarah%20E.%20Needleman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoo-job-is-especially-challenging-with-tariff-uncertainty-scotus-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20did%20nothing%20for%20my%20flexibility%20but%20take%202%20Pilates%20classes%20a%20month.%20I%20improved%20by%20almost%2020%25%2C%20according%20to%20a%203D%20scan.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Person%20in%20overhead%20squat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69976c22a645d11881899fa3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22878%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20overhead%20squat%20improved%20by%2015%20points.%20The%20only%20new%20thing%20I%20did%20was%20taking%20occasional%20reformer%20Pilates%20classes.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELast%20year%2C%20I%20got%20a%203D%20mobility%20scan%20and%20learned%20I%20needed%20to%20improve%20in%20every%20movement.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20I%20got%20re-scanned%20six%20months%20later%2C%20I%20was%20shocked%20to%20learn%20that%20my%20mobility%20had%20increased.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETaking%20just%20two%20reformer%20Pilates%20classes%20a%20month%20helped%20me%20gain%20body%20awareness%20and%20stretch%20more%20often.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F3d-test-longevity-mobility-stretching-health-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E3D%20scan%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20measured%20my%20flexibility%20last%20August%2C%20hoping%20the%20predictably%20subpar%20results%20would%20finally%20inspire%20me%20to%20stretch%20more.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20I%20did%20basically%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20knowing%20my%20shoulder%20rotation%20movement%20was%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bred%26quot%3B%20zone%20%E2%80%94%20needing%20serious%20improvement%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20avoid%20future%20pain%20%E2%80%94%20it%20wasn't%20enough%20to%20get%20me%20to%20devote%20three%20minutes%20of%20light%20stretching%20before%20my%20cardio%20and%20strength%20workouts%20as%20suggested%20by%20trainers%20I%20had%20spoken%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20thing%20I%20changed%20about%20my%20routine%20was%20signing%20up%20for%20two%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftried-seven-types-pilates-strength-toning-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereformer%20Pilates%20classes%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20month%2C%20motivated%20solely%20by%20wanting%20to%20join%20my%20friends.%20(I%20never%20went%20more%20than%20that%20because%20I%20could%20only%20stand%20to%20feel%20embarrassed%20by%20my%20winded%20lunging%20twice%20a%20month.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20I%20got%20re-scanned%20nearly%20half%20a%20year%20later%2C%20I%20wasn't%20exactly%20expecting%20miraculous%20results.%20When%20Donovan%20Stewart%2C%20the%20Life%20Time%20trainer%20who%20conducted%20my%20first%20scan%2C%20said%20it'd%20be%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20do%20another%20one%20to%20see%20my%20biggest%20pain%20points%2C%20I%20dreaded%20the%20moment%20he%20summoned%20me%20over%20to%20review%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou've%20improved%20since%20last%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBy%2013%20points.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kinotek%20results%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69977389f8731049f3af6e33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20mobility%20improved%20by%2013%20points%20above%20my%20baseline%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Kinotek%20scan.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%2FKinotek%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20now%20in%20an%20overall%20%26quot%3Bgood%26quot%3B%20mobility%20range%2C%20with%20improvements%20in%20every%20area%20and%20nothing%20in%20the%20red%20zone.%20I%20guess%20even%20the%20bare%20minimum%20of%20mobility%20work%20could%20make%20an%20enormous%20difference%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeing-flexible-could-help-you-live-longer-new-science-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emy%20overall%20health%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2222cbe8e3-446b-4595-8495-0b7b1c789ca9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEven%20sporadic%20Pilates%20stretched%20me%20out%20more%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPilates%20is%20a%20full-body%20workout%2C%20developed%20by%20Joseph%20Pilates%20during%20World%20War%20I%2C%20that%20uses%20controlled%20movements%20to%20enhance%20core%20strength%2C%20breathing%20techniques%2C%20and%20balance.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoing-pilates-for-20-years-strengthened-body-throughout-life-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edirect%20flexibility%20benefits%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20it%20prioritizes%20hip%20mobility%2C%20core%20strength%2C%20and%20shoulder%20engagement.%20I%20noticed%20that%20my%20body%20felt%20more%20sore%20after%20one%20reformer%20Pilates%20class%20than%20after%20any%20other%20workout%20I%20had%20tried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20gingerly%20lowering%20myself%20to%20my%20seat%20the%20next%20day%20was%20any%20indication%2C%20I%20was%20activating%20new%20muscle%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kinotek%20scores%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699773f7e1ba468a96ac5778%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20biggest%20area%20of%20improvement%20was%20in%20my%20shoulder%20rotation.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%2FKinotek%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20trainer%20used%20Kinotek%2C%20launched%20in%202022%20as%20a%20standardized%20movement%20assessment%20that%20scans%20the%20body%20to%20detect%20range%20of%20motion.%20It%20uses%203D%20visuals%20to%20highlight%20issues%20such%20as%20asymmetry%20or%20excessive%20flexibility%2C%20which%20can%20destabilize%20joints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompetitors%20DARI%20Motion%20and%20Kinetisense%20offer%20similar%20services%20with%20their%20FDA-cleared%20medical%20motion-analysis%20devices.%20(Kinotek%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fcosmetics%2Fregistration-listing-cosmetic-product-facilities-and-products%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregistered%20with%20the%20FDA%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20means%20that%20the%20company%20can%20sell%20its%20product%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20hasn't%20been%20officially%20reviewed%20by%20the%20agency.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20my%20latest%20scan%2C%20my%20biggest%20improvements%20were%20in%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fshoulder-stretches%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshoulder%20movements%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20my%20squat%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20shoulder%20flexion%2C%20or%20raising%20my%20arms%20overhead%20and%20lowering%20them%2C%20went%20up%20by%2014%20points%2C%20going%20from%20a%20%26quot%3Bneeds%20improvement%26quot%3B%20range%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bgood%26quot%3B%20range%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20squat%20improved%20by%2015%20points%2C%20also%20moving%20from%20%26quot%3Bneeds%20improvement%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Bgood%3B%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20shoulder%20rotation%2C%20or%20holding%20my%20arms%20at%20a%2090-degree%20angle%20while%20rotating%20them%2C%20went%20from%20a%20red%2C%20%26quot%3Bpoor%26quot%3B%20score%20to%20one%20that%20needs%20improvement%2C%20up%20by%2022%20points%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnd%20I%20had%20milder%20improvements%20in%20my%20leg%20hurdles%20and%20in%20balancing%20on%20one%20leg%20while%20stretching%20out%20the%20other.%20Still%2C%20each%20one%20also%20went%20from%20%26quot%3Bneeds%20improvement%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Bgood.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20doing%20leg%20hurdle%20with%20pole%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69977074e1ba468a96ac5713%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22878%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20leg%20hurdles%20could%20use%20more%20improvement.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22320028e9-bc26-4219-b277-de9c7cc11351%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EReformer%20Pilates%20taught%20me%20more%20body%20awareness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20told%20Stewart%20that%20the%20only%20thing%20I%20did%20was%20the%20occasional%20Pilates%20class%2C%20he%20wasn't%20surprised.%20Even%20though%20I%20wasn't%20super%20consistent%2C%20he%20said%2C%20I%20was%20increasing%20my%20%26quot%3Bbody%20awareness%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20getting%20myself%20in%20the%20habit%20of%20even%20noticing%20my%20body's%20stiffness%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftried-reformer-pilates-loved-it-would-do-again-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EReformer%20Pilates%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20incorporates%20machinery%20for%20deeper%20stretches%2C%20made%20me%20realize%20how%20tight%20my%20hips%20and%20shoulders%20felt.%20Originating%20as%20an%20apparatus%20to%20help%20wounded%20WWI%20soldiers%20exercise%20while%20lying%20down%2C%20the%20Reformer%20machine%20evolved%20in%20the%20US%20throughout%20the%2020th%20century%2C%20eventually%20being%20adapted%20by%20dancers%20and%20athletes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227979%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Women%20doing%20reformer%20Pilates%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69976d54e1ba468a96ac56bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225319%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EReformer%20Pilates%2C%20which%20incorporates%20machinery%20for%20deeper%20stretches%2C%20helped%20me%20better%20feel%20how%20tight%20my%20hips%20were.%3Cp%3EThing%20Nong%20Nont%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEquipped%20with%20straps%20and%20springs%20of%20varying%20resistance%2C%20the%20machines%20helped%20me%20stretch%20deeper%20than%20before.%20The%20light%20cracking%20sound%20from%20my%20hips%20when%20I%20lengthened%20into%20a%20wide%20stretch%20was%20like%20the%20opening%20of%20an%20ancient%20crypt.%20I%20became%20obsessed%20with%20that%20feeling.%20Before%20class%20began%2C%20I%20started%20putting%20my%20legs%20into%20the%20straps%20and%20stretching%20myself%20out%20on%20my%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20at%20home%2C%20I%20began%20sitting%20on%20the%20couch%20differently%2C%20putting%20my%20feet%20together%20and%20pushing%20my%20knees%20apart%20to%20open%20my%20hips%20more.%20I%20also%20felt%20a%20little%20more%20aware%20of%20when%20I%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fupright-go-helped-posture-slouching-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslouching%20over%20my%20laptop%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20self-correcting%20and%20trying%20to%20sit%20up%20straighter%20when%20I%20caught%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217fefbc0-ef6c-46e3-9843-a35417900982%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20a%20reminder%20to%20stretch%20whenever%20I%20can%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20doing%203D%20Kinotek%20scan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69976b65f8731049f3af6d47%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22867%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20shoulder%20rotation%20improved%20by%2022%20points%20from%20doing%20more%20Pilates.%3Cp%3ECorrie%20Aune%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20spontaneous%20Pilates%20classes%20are%20better%20than%2