on-outlook-job-market-us-economy-recession-indicator-john-hussman-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJohn%20Hussman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20legendary%20permabear%20who%20called%20the%202000%20and%202008%20crashes%2C%20expresses%20a%20degree%20of%20optimism%20about%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20days%20came%20this%20week%2C%20however%2C%20when%20Hussman%20published%20his%20monthly%20market%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20of%20the%20Hussman%20Investment%20Trust%20has%20been%20consistently%20bearish%20throughout%20the%202010s%20and%202020s%2C%20warning%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-sp500-bubble-valuations-recession-treasury-yields-hussman-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epotential%20drawdowns%20of%2060%25%20or%20more%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20there%20have%20been%20rough%20patches%20for%20stocks%20during%20recent%20years%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%2035%25%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20COVID%20drawdown%20and%20the%2025%25%20decline%20amid%20the%202022%20inflation%20surge%20%E2%80%94%20the%20market%20has%20repeatedly%20bounced%20back%2C%20posting%20huge%20cumulative%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20impressive%20returns%20appear%20to%20have%20Hussman%20readjusting%20his%20calculus%20%E2%80%94%20and%20his%20mindset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHussman%20said%20he%20expanded%20his%20investment%20parameters%20by%20reducing%20his%20downside%20hedges%20to%20allow%20for%20more%20upside%20potential%2C%20even%20during%20what%20he%20deems%20bubble%20periods%2C%20like%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20recently%20came%20to%20the%20realization%20that%20I've%20been%20discriminating%20against%20the%20bubble%2C%26quot%3B%20Hussman%20wrote%20in%20his%20commentary%20titled%20%26quot%3BHow%20I%20Learned%20To%20Love%20the%20Bubble%20(Even%20Before%20it%20Bursts).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20we%20know%20that%20speculative%20bubbles%20can%20be%20filled%20with%20delusion%2C%20and%20their%20eventual%20c