%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20come%20just%202%25%20of%20the%20time%20amid%20poor%20conditions.%20Now%2C%20with%20valuations%20consistently%20high%20since%202020%2C%20they've%20come%20more%20frequently%2C%20and%20it's%20crucial%20to%20have%20exposure%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20'trap%20door'%20conditions%20have%20been%20more%20frequent%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20these%20'roses'%20appear%20in%20close%20to%2015%25%20of%20weekly%20periods%20during%20most%20recent%201-%2C%203-%2C%20and%205-year%20horizons%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BYet%20they%20easily%20account%20for%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20total%20return%20over%20these%20horizons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Hussman%20may%20be%20a%20bit%20less%20bearish%20than%20he%20was%20before%2C%20he%20said%20not%20to%20anticipate%20a%20full-blown%20shift%20to%20the%20bullish%20side%20of%20the%20aisle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20anyone%20waiting%20for%20me%20to%20turn%20bullish%20as%20their%20signal%20to%20sell%20at%20the%20bubble%20highs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BI'll%20gently%20suggest%20that%20the%20title%20of%20this%20comment%20may%20be%20as%20much%20as%20you%20can%20ever%20hope%20to%20get.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-outlook-why-wall-street-permabear-suddenly-upbeat-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771668901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6998d081efb52c8bd0de99fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-outlook-why-wall-street-permabear-suddenly-upbeat-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It's%20a%20rare%20day%20when%20John%20Hussman%2C%20the%20legendary%20permabear%20who%20called%20the%202000%20and%202008%20crashes%2C%20expresses%20a%20degree%20of%20optimism%20about%20stocks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40busi