Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20trying%20an%20old%20website%20builder%20and%20failing%2C%20I%20hired%20a%20designer%20and%20an%20engineer%20part-time%20to%20do%20it.%20They%20were%20a%20bit%20slow%2C%20so%20while%20I%20was%20waiting%2C%20I%20tried%20using%20a%20suggested%20AI%20tool%20to%20build%20my%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20have%20funding%20or%20a%20technical%20background%2C%20so%20I%20made%20a%20free%20account%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faccel-to-lead-funding-round-for-lovable-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELovable%2C%20an%20AI%20coding%20assistant%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20started%20adding%20simple%20information%20about%20the%20website%20design%2C%20and%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20the%20AI%20platform%20built%20the%20entire%20landing%20page.%20That%20was%20my%20gateway%20into%20all%20the%20things%20AI%20can%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20using%20AI%20feels%20like%20I'm%20working%20with%20the%20dumbest%20person%20I've%20ever%20met%2C%20but%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bconstraint%26quot%3B%20very%20rarely%20enters%20my%20mind%20when%20I%20think%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffounder-hired-one-employee-uses-ai-as-middle-manager-2026-01%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehow%20AI%20is%20enabling%20me%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20run%20my%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20wants%20to%20talk%20to%20founders%20of%20AI-powered%20companies%20with%20fewer%20than%2010%20workers%2C%20and%20employees%20working%20alongside%20AI%20agents%20and%20bots%2C%20to%20understand%20what%20the%20%26quot%3BTiny%20Teams%26quot%3B%20era%20really%20feels%20like%20%E2%80%94%20the%20wins%2C%20the%20fears%2C%20and%20the%20human%20skills%20that%20stand%20out.%20Share%20your%20story%20by%20filling%20out%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScO-Lptuw9eirYFmkAfOKc1aOvrFIW1jT2FzxuLJSexsTLExg%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dheader%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equick%20form%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a243ff05-c407-4e75-a064-e2e6725cebf2%5C%22%3EI%20didn't%20set%20out%20to%20build%20an%20AI-powered%20business%20%E2%80%94%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20move%20fast%20without%20hiring%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20about%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20I've%20been%20doing%20career%20coaching%20for%20product%20managers%20on%20the%20side%20of%20my%20full-time%20job.%20I%20went%20from%20zero%20clients%20to%20consistently%20having%20a%20full%20plate.%20In%202025%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20coach%20full-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20bootstrapped%2C%20and%20hiring%20full-time%20employees%20was%20way%20too%20expensive.%20Part-time%20isn't%20ideal%20either%20because%20that's%20somebody%20who%20might%20not%20fully%20understand%20my%20business%20needs%3B%20it's%20not%20their%20main%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225152%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chirstina%20Puder%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6998b1ddefb52c8bd0de93f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPuder%20doesn't%20have%20a%20background%20and%20tech%2C%20but%20AI%20helped%20her%20built%20her%20own%20website.%3Cp%3EChristopher%20Gregory-Rivera%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20building%20my%20website%2C%20I%20was%20a%20casual%20AI%20user.%20I%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-staff-6-tips-chatgpt-model-smarter-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ego%20to%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20help%20with%20ideas%2C%20writing%2C%20and%20research.%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20background%20in%20tech%2C%20and%20because%20of%20that%2C%20I%20initially%20didn't%20think%20of%20AI%20as%20an%20enabler%20for%20my%20business.%20After%20building%20my%20website%2C%20I%20discovered%20how%20useful%20AI%20could%20be%20for%20both%20my%20webpage%20and%20the%20internal%20system%20of%20my%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a9d4e08a-a790-4090-a986-fa38c59606a5%5C%22%3EFive%20free%20credits%20a%20day%20helped%20me%20build%20my%20website%20to%20scale%20my%20company%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20tried%20building%20my%20website%20before%20using%20AI%2C%20I%20probably%20put%20in%2030%20or%2040%20hours%2C%20and%20it%20turned%20out%20so%20ugly%20and%20clunky.%20Then%20I%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flovable-ceo-anton-osika-vibe-coding-creative-employees-work-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etesting%20Loveable%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20five%20free%20credits%20a%20day.%20After%20seeing%20how%20fast%20the%20AI%20tool%20worked%20and%20how%20good%20it%20looked%2C%20I%20knew%20I'd%20be%20back%20the%20next%20day%20to%20keep%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20started%20using%20Lovable%2C%20I%20think%20the%20credits%20were%20correlated%20to%20the%20number%20of%20messages%20I%20sent.%20I%20discovered%20a%20hack%20after%20I%20sent%20a%20message%20with%20a%20single%20easy%20change%20request%2C%20and%20it%20cost%20me%20a%20credit.%20In%20the%20next%20message%2C%20I%20put%20six%20requests%2C%20and%20it%20did%20all%20six%20changes%20and%20only%20took%20one%20credit%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20they've%20discovered%20that%20loophole.%20Now%2C%20credit%20usage%20seems%20more%20closely%20tied%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-uses-17-thousand-times-more-electricity-than-us-household-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eamount%20of%20power%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20request%20consumes.%20There%20are%20times%20I'm%20building%2C%20and%20I'm%20surprised%20because%20I%20won't%20realize%20I'm%20making%20such%20an%20expensive%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20sure%20how%20many%20credits%20it%20took%20to%20build%20my%20whole%20website.%20It's%20definitely%20more%20than%20five%2C%20but%20someone%20could%20build%20a%20whole%20landing%20page%20with%20five%20credits.%20They%20could%20ask%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-top-ai-chatbots-tools-claude-chatgpt-gamma-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20tool%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20make%20a%20basic%20website%20with%20three%20sections%20and%20brand%20colors%2C%20and%20I%20think%20it%20would%20honestly%20only%20take%20two%20and%20a%20half%20credits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2219ef955b-eb7a-45b2-9ff0-6e1bbdf4d162%5C%22%3EI%20still%20use%20my%205%20free%20credits%20almost%20every%20day%2C%20even%20though%20I%20have%20a%20paid%20subscription%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20switched%20to%20a%20paid%20account%2C%20and%20now%20I%20pay%20%2420%20a%20month%20for%20my%20subscription%2C%20which%20I%20don't%20think%20is%20that%20expensive.%20I%20get%20100%20credits%20a%20month%2C%20plus%20my%20five%20free%20credits%20every%20day%20that%20don't%20roll%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20started%20to%20think%20of%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuilt-steve-jobs-custom-gpt-to-make-my-business-decisions-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20tools%20as%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20I%20use%20them%20to%20their%20full%20capacity%2C%20which%20is%20why%20I%20always%20try%20to%20use%20the%20credits%20that%20don't%20roll%20over.%20It's%20the%20same%20as%20if%20I%20hired%20someone%20full-time%3A%20I'd%20want%20them%20to%20deliver%20high%20output%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it's%20been%20a%20while%20since%20I've%20given%20my%20website%20backend%20some%20love%2C%20I'll%20write%20a%20prompt%20asking%20which%20areas%20of%20the%20code%20would%20most%20benefit%20from%20a%20refactor%2C%20and%20ask%20it%20to%20rank%20them.%20Then%2C%20based%20on%20how%20many%20of%20my%20five%20credits%20I%20have%20left%2C%20I'll%20tell%20it%20which%20areas%20to%20fix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224128ce64-2aa8-4ade-b5a7-5e2fa1d143bf%5C%22%3EAI%20helped%20me%20cut%20down%20the%20time%20for%20a%20task%20from%20one%20hour%20to%20one%20minute%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20service%20I%20offer%20is%20finding%20and%20applying%20to%20jobs%20for%20clients.%20Each%20client%20has%20very%20specific%20criteria%20for%20the%20kinds%20of%20jobs%20they%20want%2C%20and%20I%20would%20manually%20search%20for%20jobs%20that%20fit%20those%20criteria%20for%20each%20client.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227151%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Christina%20Puder%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6998b18b156648bc16a89dc5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224767%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPuder%20says%20she%20used%20AI%20to%20help%20her%20reduce%20a%20task%20that%20used%20to%20take%2060%20minutes%20down%20to%20one%20minute.%3Cp%3EChristopher%20Gregory-Rivera%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20used%20to%20take%20me%20around%2060%20minutes%20a%20day%20per%20client%20just%20to%20manually%20find%20the%20right%20jobs%20to%20apply%20for.%20I%20built%20AI-driven%20automations%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-tools-doubled-income-save-me-fifteen-hours-each-week-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereduced%20search%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20one%20minute.%20Getting%2060%20minutes%20a%20day%20back%20for%20each%20of%20my%20clients%20has%20been%20a%20massive%20scale%20unlock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20really%20didn't%20think%20it%20was%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22adc660b6-d70d-495d-ae98-67c7ce2aad5f%5C%22%3ESometimes%20I%20have%20to%20go%20back%20to%20a%20human%20engineer%2C%20but%20I'm%20still%20impressed%20with%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20once%20in%20a%20while%2C%20things%20break%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-ai-chatbots-hallucinate-openai-chatgpt-anthropic-claude-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20hit%20bugs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20have%20been%20times%20when%20I'm%20building%20something%2C%20and%20I%20spend%2040%20credits%20trying%20to%20fix%20it.%20After%20a%20while%2C%20I'll%20ask%20the%20AI%20to%20completely%20remove%20the%20feature%20we're%20working%20on%20because%20we've%20hit%20a%20bug.%20I'll%20tell%20them%20that%20instead%20of%20continuing%20to%20try%20to%20dig%20our%20way%20out%2C%20we're%20just%20going%20to%20start%20from%20scratch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20once%20an%20issue%20with%20some%20logos%20on%20my%20website.%20I%20tried%20and%20tried%20to%20prompt%20it%20to%20make%20them%20all%20look%20the%20same%20size%20together%2C%20but%20it%20wouldn't%20do%20it.%20I%20eventually%20went%20back%20to%20my%20part-time%20engineer%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20fix%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20once%20in%20a%20while%2C%20I%20go%20back%20to%20that%20engineer%20and%20just%20pay%20him%20to%20fix%20one%20or%20two%20specific%20things%20that%20I%20can't%20get%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20running%20an%20AI-powered%20business%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%2C%20Agnes%20Applegate%2C%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aaapplegate%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eaapplegate%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolo-business-owner-ai-subscription-no-employees-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771668661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6998b4222237a6a8f0cd8f48%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolo-business-owner-ai-subscription-no-employees-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20solo%20founder%20used%20AI%20to%20vibe%20code%20her%20website%2C%20cut%2060-minute%20tasks%20to%20