who%20lives%20in%20Chicago.%20Her%20employment%20and%20education%20have%20been%20verified%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20This%20piece%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20decided%20to%20retrain%20as%20an%20urban%20planner%20at%2041%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20was%20taking%20a%20leap%20of%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20felt%20great%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-change-career-at-40-lawyer-experience-goals-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emaking%20the%20pivot%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20difficult%20it%20was%20to%20establish%20credibility%20in%20a%20new%20field.%20I%20assumed%20that%20my%20years%20of%20management%20experience%20in%20retail%20would%20carry%20weight%20with%20most%20employers.%20In%20reality%2C%20I%20didn't%20feel%20that%20was%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchange-mid-career-how-know-time-pivot-30s-40s-50s-2026-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echanging%20careers%20in%20my%2040s%3C%2Fa%3E%20taught%20me%20a%20lot%20about%20starting%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHave%20you%20made%20an%20unconventional%20career%20move%3F%20If%20you're%20comfortable%20discussing%20it%20with%20a%20reporter%2C%20please%20fill%20out%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FYyvcc2cBYxuveuyW6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equick%20form%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20want%20to%20hear%20from%20people%20who%20have%20stepped%20out%20of%20or%20into%20corporate%20life%20in%20nontraditional%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a1ce8f04-a1f2-468a-9aa9-504f24e472e4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeing%20a%20manager%20in%20retail%20was%20fun%2C%20and%20I%20was%20trusted%20with%20significant%20responsibilities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20college%2C%20I%20worked%20with%20non-profits%20for%20a%20few%20years%2C%20then%20fell%20into%20a%2013-year%20career%20in%20retail.%20My%20sister%20worked%20at%20Crate%20%26amp%3B%20Barrel%20and%20I%20saw%20the%20fun%20she%20had%20furnishing%20her%20home%20using%20her%20employee%20discount.%20She%20suggested%20I%20apply%20for%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20few%20weeks%20of%20being%20hired%20in%202002%2C%20at%20around%20age%2025%2C%20I%20was%20put%20on%20the%20management%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20typical%20day%2C%20I'd%20work%20both%20back-of-house%20and%20front-of-house%3A%20managing%20teams%20and%20inventory%2C%20and%20tracking%20sales.%20I%20was%20trusted%20with%20significant%20responsibilities%2C%20from%20delivering%20bad%20news%20to%20customers%20to%20helping%20open%20new%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20high-energy%2C%20fun%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20energized%20by%20how%20much%20the%20company%20cared%20about%20the%20customer%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22627d3b86-3b3d-4c2c-8a2d-81c8a907a705%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20started%20a%20new%20career%20in%20my%2040s%20when%20my%20kids%20were%20in%20elementary%20school%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAround%202011%2C%20seven%20years%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrocery-store-worker-93-years-old-john-shipton-waitrose-uk-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emy%20retail%20career%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20started%20thinking%20about%20what%20was%20next.%20There%20was%20a%20ceiling%20on%20earning%20potential%20as%20a%20store%20manager%2C%20and%20I%20wasn't%20sure%20how%20much%20longer%20the%20work%20would%20feel%20fulfilling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20considered%20getting%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaid-off-severance-money-pay-launch-startup-or-mba-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emaster's%20degree%20in%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20attended%20a%20few%20university%20information%20sessions.%20The%20courses%20didn't%20resonate%20with%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20volunteered%20on%20the%20board%20of%20the%20self-managed%20condominium%20where%20I%20lived.%20As%20part%20of%20major%20improvement%20projects%2C%20I%20navigated%20permitting%20processes%20and%20worked%20with%20contractors%2C%20designers%2C%20and%20architects.%20I%20really%20enjoyed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20there%20was%20a%20career%20built%20around%20that%20kind%20of%20work.%20I%20attended%20an%20information%20session%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Illinois%20Chicago%20about%20the%20urban%20planning%20master's%20degree.%20I%20left%20fully%20confident%20that%20it%20was%20a%20good%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22858%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kate%20Portillo%20used%20to%20work%20at%20Crate%26amp%3BBarrel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699838daf8731049f3af7522%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22796%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKate%20Portillo%20used%20to%20work%20at%20Crate%20%26amp%3B%20Barrel.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kate%20Portillo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I%20was%20accepted%20on%20to%20the%20course%20and%20understood%20the%20level%20of%20commitment%20involved%2C%20I%20resigned%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrate-and-barrel-best-things-there-interior-decorator-says-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECrate%20%26amp%3B%20Barrel%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20began%20the%20program%20in%202016.%20I%20was%2042%2C%20and%20both%20my%20kids%20were%20in%20elementary%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20parents%20went%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoing-back-to-college-daughter-classmate-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eback%20to%20school%3C%2Fa%3E%20later%20in%20life%20%E2%80%94%20my%20father%20earned%20a%20master's%20degree%20in%20public%20health%2C%20and%20my%20mom%20earned%20one%20in%20education%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20think%20that%20inspired%20me.%20I%20was%20happy%20my%20own%20children%20would%20see%20that%20life%20is%20not%20