0extreme%20conditions%20from%20turbulence%20to%20low-visibility%20landings.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20flew%20an%20Airbus%20A350%20simulator%20at%20Turkish%20Airlines'%20training%20center%20in%20Istanbul.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20mimicked%20anomalies%20like%20wind%20shear%2C%20extreme%20turbulence%2C%20and%20traffic%20avoidance.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESimulators%20let%20airlines%20safely%20train%20pilots%20for%20rare%20but%20high-risk%20scenarios%20they%20may%20face.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20takes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-pilot-thirty-years-career-salary-pay-captain-airlines-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eairline%20pilots%3C%2Fa%3E%20years%20to%20go%20from%20their%20first%20discovery%20flight%20to%20sitting%20in%20the%20cockpit%20of%20a%20commercial%20jetliner%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20then%2C%20the%20training%20never%20stops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20a%20pilot's%20professional%20life%20is%20spent%20outside%20the%20cockpit%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-737-max-simulator-what-its-like-to-be-pilot-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehigh-tech%20simulators%20that%20mimic%20real%20flights%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20giant%20boxes%20mounted%20on%20hydraulic%20legs%20allow%20pilots%20to%20safely%20train%20for%20stalls%2C%20engine%20fires%2C%20and%20other%20emergency%20scenarios%20in%20a%20controlled%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recently%20flew%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarlux-a350-1000-new-aircraft-business-class-seats-taiwan-airline-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAirbus%20A350%3C%2Fa%3E%20simulator%20at%20Turkish%20Airlines'%20flight%20training%20center%20in%20Istanbul.%20With%20the%20help%20of%20Captain%20Fatih%20Altunok%2C%20the%20SVP%20of%20flight%20training%2C%20I%20navigated%20airports%2C%20severe%20weather%2C%20traffic%20conflicts%2C%20and%20turbulence%2C%20and%20practiced%20takeoffs%2C%20landings%2C%20and%20emergency%20scenarios.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225561%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20outside%20of%20Turkish%20Airlines'%20flight%20training%20center.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699882deefb52c8bd0de8d06%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224171%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIstanbul%20was%20unusually%20snowy%20on%20the%20day%20of%20my%20visit.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20other%20major%20airlines%20worldwide%2C%20Turkish%20Airlines'%20pilot%20training%20program%20is%20built%20around%20international%20standards%20that%20require%20thousands%20of%20hours%20of%20flight%20time%2C%20regular%20medical%20exams%2C%20and%20recurrent%20simulator%20checks%20to%20expose%20them%20to%20rare%20but%20high-risk%20scenarios.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltunok%20said%20Turkish%20Airlines'%20over%205%2C000%20pilots%20(including%20320%20foreign%20pilots%20from%2058%20countries)%20each%20spend%20months%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-airlines-flight-academy-pilot-training-simulators-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einitial%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20flying%20passengers%2C%20and%20must%20complete%20four%20hours%20of%20simulator%20training%20every%206%20months%20for%20recurrent%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20regulators%20mandate%20recurrent%20simulator%20training%20for%20airline%20pilots%20every%20six%20to%2012%20months%2C%20typically%20in%20one%20or%20more%20four-hour%20blocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Turkish%20fligh%20tsimulator.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699887deefb52c8bd0de8e05%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETurkish%20Airlines%20said%20it%20expects%20to%20acquire%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20more%20simulators%20by%20the%20early%202030s.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAltunok%20said%20the%20flight%20simulator%20mirrors%20the%20exact%20configuration%20of%20a%20Turkish%20A350.%20I%20noticed%20that%20every%20switch%2C%20button%2C%20lever%2C%20screen%2C%20and%20alarm%20is%20carefully%20calibrated%2C%20and%20the%20legs%20tilt%20and%20lift%20the%20simulator%20to%20create%20lifelike%20movements%20throughout%20every%20phase%20of%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wraparound%20screens%20were%20my%20only%20cue%20that%20it%20was%20fake.%20The%20visuals%20%E2%80%94%20simplified%20clouds%2C%20terrain%2C%20roads%2C%20buildings%2C%20and%20airports%20%E2%80%94%20aren't%20photo-realistic%2C%20though%20that's%20by%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20imagery%20prioritizes%20stable%20frame%20rates%20and%20low%20latency%20while%20providing%20pilots%20with%20the%20critical%20visual%20cues%20needed%20to%20judge%20things%20like%20altitude%2C%20runway%20alignment%2C%20and%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20runway%20simulation%20on%20A350%20flight%20sim.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699884932237a6a8f0cd881b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhat%20the%20runway%20looked%20like%20on%20the%20simulator's%20wraparound%20screens.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAltunok%20said%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsee-inside-a-boeing-787-dreamliner-flight-simulator-pilot-training-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esimulator's%20hydraulic%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20can't%20reproduce%20every%20sensation%20of%20flight%2C%20but%20it%20uses%20a%20combination%20of%20motion%2C%20visual%2C%20auditory%2C%20and%20tactile%20cues%20to%20trick%20the%20brain%2C%20from%20normal%20takeoffs%2C%20landings%2C%20and%20turbulence%20to%20more%20extreme%20maneuvers%20%E2%80%94%20including%20flipping%20the%20jet%20upside%20down%2C%20which%20he%20even%20demonstrated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20simulator%20I%20used%20was%20one%20of%20about%2030%20in%20use%2C%20run%20by%20a%20team%20of%20about%20650%20instructors.%20They%20run%20seven%20days%20a%20week%2C%20365%20days%20a%20year.%20The%20airline%20said%20in%202025%20alone%2C%20the%20simulators%20trained%207%2C500%20pilots%20individually%20(some%20more%20than%20once)%20and%20collectively%20ran%20for%20160%2C000%20hours%20%E2%80%94%20or%20over%2018%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20sessions%20let%20airlines%20regularly%20assess%20pilot%20proficiency%20and%20reinforce%20their%20safety%20culture%2C%20while%20crew%20can%20fine-tune%20their%20skills.%20Here's%20what%20it%20felt%20like%20to%20be%20at%20the%20controls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ec44217c-52b6-4e87-b980-f5f002917b23%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20simulated%20jet%20felt%20massive%20and%20loud%2C%20even%20in%20the%20box%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20routine%20tasks%20revealed%20how%20technical%20the%20job%20is.%20Taxiing%20a%20half-million-pound%20plane%20from%20gate%20to%20runway%20requires%20constant%20adjustments%2C%20and%20the%20takeoff%20was%20more%20intense%20than%20I%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflew-9-hours-europe-best-airline-economy-cabin-turkish-food-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20fly%20as%20a%20passenger%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20least%20twice%20a%20month%2C%20so%20I%20know%20the%20feeling%20of%20a%20jet%20barreling%20down%20the%20runway%2C%20but%20the%20simulated%20engines%20felt%20surprisingly%20loud%20and%20powerful%20in%20that%20training%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltunok%20took%20the%20right%20seat%20and%20let%20me%20sit%20in%20the%20captain's%20position%20on%20the%20left%2C%20talking%20me%20through%20the%20takeoff.%20I%20felt%20the%20runway%20bumps%20and%20a%20brief%20G-force%20as%20we%20lifted%20off%20%E2%80%94%20though%20even%20in%20an%20A350%2C%20you%20pull%20back%20on%20the%20sidestick%20more%20gently%20than%20you'd%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20in%20the%20air%2C%20we%20flew%20a%20virtual%20circuit%20around%20Istanbul.%20The%20screens%20recreated%20the%20landscape%20below%2C%20letting%20me%20look%20down%20on%20the%20city%20and%20the%20Bosphorus%20Strait%20as%20if%20I%20were%20actually%20above%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20is%20what%20the%20virtual%20landscape%20looked%20like%20with%20water%20and%20terrain.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69988c0d156648bc16a89890%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20is%20what%20the%20virtual%20landscape%20looked%20like%20on%20the%20screens.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20given%20a%20very%20simple%20setup%3A%20just%20keep%20the%20plane%20on%20course%20using%20the%20sidestick%20while%20Altunok%20%E2%80%94%20who%20has%20flown%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-777x-compared-airbus-a350-differences-widebody-which-better-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAirbus%20and%20Boeing%20jets%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Turkish%20Airlines%20for%2020%20years%20%E2%80%94%20handled%20the%20flaps%2C%20engine%20power%2C%20and%20the%20myriad%20other%20tasks%20required%20of%20the%20crew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20eventually%20let%20autopilot%20take%20over.%20It%20was%20fun%20to%20watch%20the%20process%20and%20experience%20flying%20from%20a%20perspective%20that%20few%20travelers%20ever%20get.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20noticed%20the%20muscle%20memory%20pilots%20must%20develop%20between%20actually%20flying%20the%20plane%2C%20quickly%20flipping%20to%20certain%20checklists%2C%20and%20reacting%20safely%20to%20sudden%20alerts%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funited-airlines-emergency-landing-sfo-hongkong-smoke-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eemergency%20situations%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20instructor%2C%20who%20sits%20behind%20the%20cockpit%20with%20their%20own%20computer%20setup%2C%20sent%20a%20few%20my%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20a%20traffic%20alert%20that%20another%20plane%20came%20too%20close%20for%20comfort%20after%20takeoff.%20Sometimes%20this%20is%20just%20an%20alert%3B%20other%20times%2C%20the%20pilots%20are%20given%20a%20command%20to%20change%20altitude%20or%20adjust%20speed%20to%20avoid%20a%20collision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20were%20returning%20to%20Istanbul%20Airport%20in%20rough%20weather%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwo-recent-airline-incidents-are-reminder-of-vital-safety-rules-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eturbulence%20and%20all%20jolting%20the%20jet%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20loud%2C%20red%20%26quot%3Bwindshear%26quot%3B%20alert%20blared%20in%20the%20cockpit.%20Windshear%20is%20a%20sudden%20change%20in%20wind%20speed%20or%20direction%2C%20often%20near%20the%20ground%2C%20that%20can%20cause%20a%20rapid%20loss%20of%20lift%20and%20has%20caused%20past%20plane%20crashes.%20Airbus%20makes%20the%20warning%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20miss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20in%20the%20A350%20sim.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69988537efb52c8bd0de8d91%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20photo%20of%20took%20of%20me%20landing%20in%20low%20visibility.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20alert%20cues%20a%20go-around%2C%20and%20Altunok%20instructed%20me%20to%20push%20the%20engines%20to%20full%20throttle%20and%20climb%20away%20from%20the%20runway%3B%20I%20could%20feel%20the%20engines%20rev.%20Pilots%20must%20instinctively%20do%20this%20within%20just%20a%20few%20seconds%2C%20then%20reconfigure%20the%20aircraft%20and%20communicate%20with%20air%20traffic%20control%20for%20another%20landing%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimulators%20also%20train%20pilots%20on%20automated%20systems.%20On%20one%20landing%2C%20Altunok%20set%20up%20and%20executed%20an%20auto-landing.%20Watching%20him%20manage%20it%20showed%20how%20pilots%20must%20prepare%20for%20low-visibility%20approaches%20and%20constantly%20monitor%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnowing%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flatam-boeing-787-plunged-reminder-always-wear-seatbelt-turbulence-safety-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eturbulence%20often%20feels%20more%20intense%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20it%20actually%20is%2C%20I%20asked%20the%20instructor%20to%20show%20me%20what%20extreme%20turbulence%20would%20be%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20bouncing%20in%20my%20seat%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20difficult%20to%20keep%20my%20hands%20steady%20on%20the%20controls.%20The%20autopilot%20helped%20keep%20the%20jet%20stable%2C%20and%20we%20weren't%20losing%20hundreds%20of%20feet%20of%20altitude%20with%20every%20bump%2C%20as%20some%20passengers%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221178%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22My%20screen%20during%20the%20turbulence%20showing%20the%20altitude.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699889012237a6a8f0cd88f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22911%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20was%20my%20screen%20during%20the%20turbulence%2C%20showing%20the%20altitude%2C%20heading%2C%20and%20weather%20conditions.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAltunok%20said%20that%20in%20turbulence%2C%20the%20pilots'%20main%20goal%20is%20to%20find%20smoother%20air%20%E2%80%94%20both%20to%20keep%20passengers%20comfortable%20and%20to%20avoid%20spilling%20coffee%20on%20their%20uniforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rigorous%20simulator%20and%20overall%20training%20programs%20directly%20feed%20into%20the%20airline's%20safety%20reco