rders.%20Some%20are%20taking%20a%20wait-and-see%20mentality%2C%20or%20they%20just%20don't%20want%20to%20pay%20the%20extra%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComics%20themselves%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lot%20of%20which%20are%20printed%20in%20Canada%20%E2%80%94%20have%20not%20been%20impacted%20by%20tariffs.%20But%20for%20me%20and%20for%20other%20comic%20book%20stores%2C%20action%20figures%2C%20board%20games%2C%20and%20comic%20book%20supplies%2C%20like%20storage%20items%2C%20are%20being%20impacted.%20Action%20figures%20account%20for%20about%2065%25%20of%20my%20shop's%20revenue%2C%20and%20they%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fafina-shower-head-founder-tests-paying-more-american-made-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emade%20in%20China%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20these%20orders%20are%20made%20far%20in%20advance%2C%20too.%20We%20were%20being%20charged%20tariffs%20on%20items%20ordered%20in%202023%20and%202024.%20There's%20stuff%20I%20need%20to%20order%20next%20week%20that%20ships%20in%20June%20of%202027.%20Is%20the%20tariff%20going%20to%20be%206%25%3F%20Is%20it%20going%20to%20be%20zero%3F%20Is%20it%20going%20to%20be%20100%25%3F%20I%20have%20no%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22892%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Marc%20Bowker%20and%20his%20family%20in%20front%20of%20his%20store%2C%20Alter%20Ego%20Comics.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69991643156648bc16a8a738%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22669%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMarc%20Bowker%20and%20his%20family%20in%20front%20of%20his%20store.%3Cp%3EMarc%20Bowker%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b0bbc2ff-07aa-45cb-a664-fd03959111d5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20unclear%20if%20small%20businesses%20will%20get%20refunds%20or%20what%20will%20happen%20next%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20tariff%20costs%20small%20businesses%20have%20already%20paid%2C%20are%20we%20getting%20that%20back%3F%20Probab